0at%20the%20head%20of%20the%20able%20is%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20maroon%20sweater%20with%20white%20button%20down%20shirt%20underneath.%20Both%20people%20are%20visible%20from%20the%20nose%20down%20and%20are%20out%20of%20focus.%20There%20are%20white%20china%20plates%20in%20front%20of%20everyone%20with%20forks.%20On%20the%20table%20is%20a%20red%20runner%20with%20decorative%20pine%20cones%2C%20various%20snacks%20in%20bowls%20and%20on%20plates.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656dfd7f58e7c0c29a293ca6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStaying%20sober%20during%20the%20holidays%20can%20be%20tough%2C%20especially%20early%20in%20recovery.%3Cp%3Eurbazon%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThree%20mental-health%20professionals%20described%20strategies%20for%20avoiding%20alcohol%20this%20time%20of%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20suggested%20having%20a%20sober%20buddy%2C%20keeping%20a%20drink%20in%20your%20hand%2C%20and%C2%A0setting%20boundaries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20said%20that%20reminding%20yourself%20of%20your%20reasons%20for%20staying%20sober%20can%20help%20head%20off%20temptation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20sobriety%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftimeline-of-the-sober-curious-movement-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eon%20the%20rise%20among%20Gen%20Zers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20holidays%20can%20be%20a%20minefield%20of%20temptation%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20seems%20like%20everyone%20around%20you%20is%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.embodiedwellnesstherapy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESarah%20Rollins%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20licensed%20social%20worker%2C%20said%20that%20staying%20sober%20during%20the%20holidays%20can%20be%20difficult%20for%20a%20few%20reasons.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20free%20time%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20chaos%20of%20the%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20an%20expectation%20around%20the%20holidays%20to%20be%20with%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollins%20said%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20around%20family%20sober%20can%20be%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20particularly%20early%20in%20recovery%20or%20soon%20after%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20loved%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20strategies%20can%20help%20mitigate%20the%20temptation%20to%20drink%20with%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBring%20a%20sober%20buddy%20or%20supporter%20with%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20another%20person%20who's%20committed%20to%20keeping%20you%20sober%20can%20be%20helpful%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.columbiapsychiatry.org%2Fprofile%2Fryan-s-sultan-md%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDr.%20Ryan%20Sultan%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Sultan%20Lab%20for%20Mental%20Health%20Informatics%20at%20Columbia%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAttend%20gatherings%20with%20a%20friend%20who's%20also%20sober%20or%20understands%20your%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20Sultan%20said.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20presence%20can%20offer%20support%20and%20strength.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdecisiveelementpsychotherapy.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPaula%20Lamanna%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20licensed%20social%20worker%2C%20said%20that%20if%20you%20can't%20bring%20a%20plus-one%C2%A0who's%20willing%20to%20stay%20sober%20with%20you%2C%20%26quot%3Btry%20to%20have%20someone%20available%20by%20phone%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20friend%20or%20a%20sponsor.%26quot%3B%20Speak%20with%20the%20person%20before%20heading%20to%20the%20party%20so%20they're%20clear%20on%20the%20kind%20of%20support%20you%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKeep%20a%20drink%20in%20your%20hand%20to%20avoid%20offers%20for%20refills%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERollins%20said%20that%20having%20a%20nonalcoholic%20drink%20in%20hand%20all%20night%20can%20stop%20others%20from%20offering%20to%20fetch%20you%20a%20drink%20or%20pressuring%20you%20to%20have%20a%20full%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAsk%20for%20a%20nonalcoholic%20drink%20like%20a%20mocktail%20or%20something%20that%20might%20look%20more%20alcoholic%20so%20no%20one%20knows%20that%20you're%20not%20drinking%2C%26quot%3B%20Rollins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20bring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Freviewing-favorite-nonalcoholic-cocktail-recipes-from-popular-chefs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emocktail%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20home%20or%20find%20ingredients%20at%20a%20party%20to%20make%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPrepare%20your%20responses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20aren't%20ready%20to%20share%20your%20sobriety%20journey%2C%20having%20a%20story%20you've%20rehearsed%20a%20few%20times%20can%20help%20quickly%20stop%20conversations%20about%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20feel%20comfortable%20telling%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Lamanna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbe%20prepared%20with%20a%20cover%20story%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20on%20antibiotics%2C%20you%20have%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20doing%20a%20cleanse%2C%20stomach%20problems%2C%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20someone%20pressures%20you%2C%20Sultan%20said%2C%20assert%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-right-way-to-set-boundaries-with-people-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboundaries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20OK%20to%20firmly%20yet%20politely%20decline%20offers%20to%20drink%2C%26quot%3B%20Sultan%20said.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20few%20rehearsed%20responses%20can%20be%20helpful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECommunicate%20your%20needs%20and%20have%20an%20exit%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20want%20to%20support%20their%20loved%20ones%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20coworkers%20on%20the