e-viral-on-internet-for-their-shocking-price-see-details-4710294%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Flouis-vuittons-earphones-are-viral-on-internet-for-their-shocking-price-see-details-4710294%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Flouis-vuittons-earphones-are-viral-on-internet-for-their-shocking-price-see-details-4710294%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Criminal%20Code%20Bills%20Passed%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%20With%20Most%20Opposition%20MPs%20Suspended%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20crucial%20bills%20that%20would%20replace%20India's%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%2C%20virtually%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20Opposition.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20(Second)%20Sanhita%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20(Second)%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20(Second)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20of%201860%2C%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20of%201973%20and%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%20of%201872.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20laws%20were%20passed%20without%20any%20substantial%20debate%20owing%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20143%20Opposition%20members%20following%20protests%20over%20the%20recent%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20of%20suspensions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20reached%2097%20today%2C%20with%20the%20suspension%20of%20two%20more%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20snowballed%20into%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition%20following%20the%20mimicry%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20and%20Vice%20President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20by%20a%20Trinamool%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsisting%20that%20the%20new%20laws%20will%20replace%20the%20colonial%20era%20rules%20that%20are%20completely%20unsuitable%20for%20this%20day%20and%20age%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20today%20that%20the%20new%20bills%20lay%20%26quot%3Bemphasis%20on%20Indianness%2C%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20and%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20gone%20through%20every%20comma%2C%20full%20stop%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20insisting%20that%20they%20were%20in%20consonance%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bills%20were%20withdrawn%20after%20the%20monsoon%20session%20and%20three%20new%20bills%20introduced%2C%20as%20a%20few%20changes%20were%20to%20be%20made%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20new%20bills%20have%20been%20examined%20by%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20and%20instead%20of%20coming%20up%20with%20official%20amendments%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20bring%20the%20bills%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20alleged%20that%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20is%20the%20government's%20ploy%20to%20pass%20key%20bills%20without%20any%20discussion.%20The%20criminal%20law%20bills%20were%20vehemently%20criticised%20by%20several%20Opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20the%20DMK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20wanted%20a%20larger%20public%20debate%20on%20the%20bills%20that%20would%20involve%20judges%2C%20jurists%2C%20lawyers%2C%20criminologists%20and%20other%20stakeholders%20including%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parties%20further%20said%20that%20many%20sections%20of%20the%20new%20criminal%20bills%20are%20identical%20to%20the%20colonial%20laws%20that%20the%20government%20claimed%20to%20have%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20also%20criticised%20the%20Hindi%20names%20of%20the%20laws%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20%C3%A4ffront%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20non-Hindi%20speaking%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20wanted%20the%20bills%20passed%20after%20the%20general%20elections%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3