6quot%3B%20He%20shared%20the%20story%20of%20his%20search%20for%20his%20birth%20father%20in%20the%20BBC%20documentary%20%26quot%3BA%20Stranger%20in%20My%20Family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20had%20felt%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20place%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20%26quot%3Bown%20body%20and%20life%26quot%3B%20before%20doing%20the%20test%2C%20and%20he%20said%20in%20the%20documentary%20that%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20because%20he%20is%20gay.%20But%20he%20still%20felt%20different%20after%20he%20came%20out%20to%20his%20parents%2C%20so%20he%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20DNA%20test%20to%20learn%20about%20his%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20tests%20work%20by%20comparing%20variants%20in%20the%20subject's%20DNA%20to%20the%20frequencies%20of%20different%20variants%20in%20populations%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20Davies'%20ancestors%20on%20both%20his%20parents'%20side%20were%20from%20near%20Manchester%2C%20as%20far%20as%20he%20knew%2C%20and%20he%20grew%20up%20identifying%20as%20white%20British.%20The%20test%2C%20however%2C%20produced%20a%20result%20of%2022.5%25%20West%20African%2C%2032.5%25%20Iberian%2C%2023.4%25%20English%2C%209.4%25%20Scandinavian%2C%20with%20the%20remaining%2012.2%25%20labelled%20as%20%26quot%3Bthree%20more%20ethnicities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDavies'%20mother%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20Portuguese%20man%20while%20on%20vacation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Davies%20asked%20his%20mother%2C%20Liz%20Davies%2C%20about%20his%20results%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20she%20had%20had%20a%20fling%20with%20a%20bartender%20while%20on%20vacation%20in%20Albufeira%2C%20Portugal%2C%2030%20years%20earlier%2C%20during%20the%20early%20days%20of%20her%20relationship%20with%20the%20man%20Davies%20had%20thought%20was%20his%20biological%20father.%20No%20one%20questioned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwoman-found-out-dad-isnt-biological-father-family-argument-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epaternit