cked%20down%20his%20father%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20himself%20at%20a%20dead%20end%20in%20investigating%20his%20DNA%20test%20matches%2C%20Davies%20went%20to%20visit%20Albufeira.%20He%20went%20with%20a%20friend%20of%20his%20mother's%20who%20had%20been%20on%20vacation%20with%20her%20when%20Davies%20was%20conceived%2C%20hoping%20she%20could%20identify%20the%20bar%20where%20Carlos%20had%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20did%2C%20and%20House%20tracked%20Carlos%20down%20using%20the%20bar's%20old%20employee%20records.%20He%20agreed%20to%20a%20paternity%20test%20to%20see%20whether%20he%20was%20in%20fact%20Davies'%20father.%20It%20came%20back%20positive%2C%20and%20the%20two%20agreed%20to%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20had%20an%20emotional%20reunion%20in%20London.%20Carlos%20immediately%20accepted%20Davies%20when%20he%20came%20out%20to%20him%20and%20later%20introduced%20him%20to%20his%20other%20two%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlos%20also%20told%20Davies%20that%20he%20hadn't%20known%20Oliveira%2C%20who%20had%20left%20Guinea-Bissau%20after%20the%20war.%20He%20said%20his%20mother%20had%20never%20told%20him%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20her%20relationship%20with%20his%20father%2C%20or%20his%20own%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDavies%20gained%20another%20family%20and%20got%20closer%20to%20the%20one%20he%20already%20had%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDavies%20has%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20his%20multiracial%20identity%2C%20and%20has%20incorporated%20his%20birth%20grandfather's%20surname%2C%20Oliveira%2C%20into%20his%20surname%20to%20honor%20his%20heritage.%20Davies%20said%20that%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20birth%20father%20and%20brothers%20%26quot%3Bhas%20gone%20from%20strength%20to%20strength.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20test%20results%20%26quot%3Bcaused%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20pain%20for%20the%20first%20year%20or%20so%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20immediate%20family%2C%20because%20he%20had%20to%20tell%20the%20father%20who%20raised%20him%20about%20his%20mom's%20infidelity.%20But%20the%20documentary%20forced%20them%20to%20confront%20the%20situation%2C%20and%20now%20he%20would%20consider%20them%20to%20be%20the%20closest%20they've%20ever%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20the%20past%20that%20I%20belong%20to%2C%20and%20build%20connections%20with%20family%20I've%20never%20known%20in%20the%20process%2C%20I%20feel%20healed%20and%20changed%20in%20ways%20that%20are%20hard%20to%20explain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20most%20excited%20to%20share%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20with%20my%20blended%20family%2C%20and%20to%20step%20into%20the%20next%20chapter%20of%20my%20life%20feeling%20secure%20in%20who%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20previously%20reported%20on%20others%20who%20have%20learned%20they%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhome-dna-tests-different-race-discovery-paternity-shock-lies-2022-09%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edifferent%20racial%20identities%20than%20they%20expected%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20thanks%20to%20DNA%20tests.%20But%20these%20tests%20can%20expose%20many%20other%20secrets%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20for%20a%20couple%20who%20discovered%20they%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcolorado-couple-finds-out-they-are-related-after-dna-test%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecousins%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20two%20men%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftwo-canadian-men-switched-at-birth-1955-dna-test-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eswitched%20at%20birth%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20man%20even%20learned%20that%20his%20father%20had%20been%20a%20wanted%20murderer%20who%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhome-dna-test-reveals-murderer-father-escaped-criminal-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ekilled%20his%20own%20parents%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20escaping%20prison%20and%