y%20and%20how%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Mysuru%20facilitated%20entry%20of%20two%20intruders%20into%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20December%2013th%20-%20who%20are%20now%20charged%20under%20the%20anti-terror%20law%20UAPA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-respect-for-jagdeep-dhankhar-mimicry-an-art-mp-kalyan-banerjee-after-huge-row-4708007%5C%22%3EPM%20Did%20It%20Too%2C%20Says%20Trinamool%20MP%2C%20Defending%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20Mimicry%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20ecosystem%20is%20also%20silent%20on%20the%20summary%20suspension%20of%20142%20MPs%20for%20making%20a%20perfectly%20legitimate%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20more%20opposition%20MPs%20were%20suspended%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20number%20to%20143.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Disrespecting%20The%20Post'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Vice-President%20Dhankhar%20said%20the%20mimicry%20by%20Serampore%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20and%20its%20filming%20by%20Mr%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar-kalyan-banerjee-suspension-of-mps-insult-of-my-jat-farmer-background-veep-dhankhar-after-mp-mimics-him-4703351%5C%22%3Ewas%20an%20insult%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20farmers%20and%20the%20Jat%20community.%20Addressing%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20P%20Chidambaram%2C%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20had%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%2C%20you%20are%20a%20very%20senior%20member.%20Imagine%20what%20I%20felt%20when%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20your%20party%2C%20an%20MP%2C%20was%20filming%20an%20act%20making%20fun%20of%20me%2C%20a%20personal%20attack.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20just%20the%20insult%20of%20a%20farmer%20or%20a%20community%2C%20it's%20disrespect%20to%20the%20post%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman.%20And%20that%20t