-single-crash-lifetime%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Fox%20News%20Digital%20in%20an%20interview%20published%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20and%20financial%20historian%20blamed%20excessive%20government%20spending%20in%20recent%20years%20for%20creating%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20bubble%26quot%3B%20in%20asset%20prices%20that%20he's%20certain%20will%20burst.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20fell%20sharply%20last%20year%2C%20but%20has%20rebounded%20by%20nearly%2025%25%20this%20year%20to%20trade%20just%20shy%20of%20its%20all-time%20high.%20House%20prices%20have%20also%20surged%20to%20record%20highs%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20while%20bitcoin%20and%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20in%20value%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20crash%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20correction%2C%26quot%3B%20Dent%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20in%20the%20'29%20to%20'32%20level.%20And%20anybody%20who%20sat%20through%20that%20would%20have%20shot%20their%20stockbroker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20newsletter%20writer%20and%20founder%20of%20HS%20Dent%20Investment%20Management%20suggested%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20could%20plummet%20by%20over%2080%25%20to%20its%20lowest%20level%20since%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20the%20average%20US%20house%20price%20could%20be%20cut%20in%20half%2C%20and%20cryptos%20could%20nosedive%20by%20over%2090%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeclines%20of%20that%20magnitude%20might%20make%20authorities%20think%20twice%20about%20running%20budget%20deficits%20and%20artificially%20inflating%20asset%20prices%20in%20the%20future%2C%20Dent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20the%20guy%20that's%20praying%20for%20a%20crash%20while%20everybody%20else%20is%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20should%20be%20a%20lesson%20I%20don't%20think%20we'll%20ever%20revisit.%20I%20don't%20think%20we'll%20ever%20see%20a%20bubble%20for%20any%20of%20our%20lifetimes%20again.%26quot%3B%3C