the%20Fed's%20rate%20hikes%20is%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDent%20has%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20they've%20defied%20his%20doom%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fharry-dent-stock-market-bubble-asset-prices-crash-economy-depression-2022-8%5C%22%3Ewarned%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20that%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20would%20crash%20by%20over%2040%25%20to%20below%208%2C000%20points%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20months.%20The%20tech-heavy%20index%20did%20slump%20as%20low%20as%2010%2C300%20points%20in%20October%20that%20year%2C%20but%20it%20has%20rallied%20since%20then%20to%20over%2015%2C000%20points%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks-crypto-house-prices-dent-market-outlook-bubble-crash-recession-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703074871000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F52ae23f669beddc04a70d7f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstocks-crypto-house-prices-dent-market-outlook-bubble-crash-recession-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Caveat%3A%20Dent%20has%20been%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20on%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20they've%20defied%20his%20doom%20saying.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstocks-crypto-house-prices-dent-market-outlook-bubble-crash-recession-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BItalian%20Mindset%20Won't%20Understand%20Indian%20Laws%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20Jabs%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20three%20bills%20to%20replace%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20seek%20to%20bring%20comprehensive%20changes%20to%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20with%20a%20human-centric%20approach%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20imparting%20justice%20instead%20of%20imposing%20penalties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20(Second)%20Sanhita%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20(Second)%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20(Second)%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Shah%20said%20the%20three%20proposed%20laws%20also%20have%20a%20clear%20definition%20of%20terrorism%2C%20scrap%20sedition%20as%20a%20crime%20and%20introduce%20a%20new%20section%20titled%20%26quot%3Boffenses%20against%20the%20state%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20three%20bills%20were%20drafted%20after%20comprehensive%20consultations%20and%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20through%20every%20comma%20and%20full%20stop%20of%20the%20draft%20legislations%20before%20bringing%20them%20before%20the%20House%20for%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20existing%20criminal%20laws%20-%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20and%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20-%20were%20reflective%20of%20the%20colonial%20mindset%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20punish%20and%20not%20impart%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20three%20news%20bills%20seek%20to%20establish%20a%20justice%20system%20based%20on%20Indian%20thinking...%20Three%20proposed%20criminal%20laws%20will%20free%20people%20from%20colonial%20mindset%20and%20its%20symbols%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20seeks%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code-1860%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20will%20replace%20the%20CrPC%20of%201973%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Bill%20will%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%20of%201872.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20will%20have%20the%20human%20touch.%20Till%20we%20repeal%20these%20old%20laws%2C%20we%20are%20still%20following%20laws%20made%20by%20the%20UK%20government.%20We%20still%20use%20English%20words%20like%20Her%20Majesty%2C%20British%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20crown%2C%20barrister%2C%20ruler%20after%2075%20years%20of%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20minister%20said%20the%20colonial-era%20laws%20prioritised%20acts%20of%20%26quot%3Blooting%20the%20treasury%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Buprooting%20rail%20tracks%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binsult%20to%20the%20Crown%26quot%3B%20over%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20children%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20border%20security%2C%20and%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20old%20laws%20had%20listed%20rape%20under%20Section%20375-376%2C%20the%20new%20bill%20has%20the%20crime%20listed%20under%20Section%2063%2C%20murder%20was%20listed%20under%20Section%20302%20now%20it%20is%20Section%20101%2C%20kidnapping%20was%20under%20Section%20359%20and%20now%20it%20is%20Section%20136%2C%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20the%20features%20of%20the%20bills%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20bill%20punishes%20mob%20lynching%20with%20death%20penalty.%20(Congress%20leader%20P)%20Chidambaram%20kept%20asking%20me%20what%20about%20mob%20lynching.%20He%20does%20not%20understand%20BJP%20and%20our%20mentality.%20Why%20did%20you%20not%20penalise%20mob%20lynching%20during%20your%20rule%3F%20If%20one's%20mind%20is%20Indian%2C%20you%20will%20understand%20the%20laws.%20If%20it%20is%20Italian%2C%20you%20won't.%26quot%3B%20The%20three%20bills%20reflect%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Constitution...but%20those%20with%20an%20Italian%20mindset%20will%20never%20understand%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20apparent%20dig%20at%20the%20opposition%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20asserted%20that%20the%20three%20laws%20were%20based%20on%20justice%2C%20transparency%20and%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20government%20which%20has%20fulfilled%20the%20promises%20it%20has%20mentioned%20in%20its%20manifesto.%20We%20have%20revoked%20Article%20370%2C%20removed%20AFSPA%20in%2070%20per%20cent%20areas%20in%20the%20northeastern%20states%2C%20banned%20triple%20talaq%20and%20gave%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20women%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703074620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fpqj6i6f8_parliament_625x300_20_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-new-criminal-laws-seek-to-put-in-place-human-centric-justice-system-amit-shah-4709762%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20the%20three%20bills%20to%20replace%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20seek%20to%20bring%20comprehensive%20changes%20to%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20with%20a%20human-centric%20approach%20and%20a%20focus%20on%20imparting%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-new-criminal-laws-seek-to-put-in-place-human-centric-justice-system-amit-shah-4709762%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-new-criminal-laws-seek-to-put-in-place-human-centric-justice-system-amit-shah-4709762%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthree-new-criminal-laws-seek-to-put-in-place-human-centric-justice-system-amit-shah-4709762%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taimur%20prays%20to%20Lord%20Shiva%20with%20sister%20Inaaya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe