Compared%20to%20the%20regular%20Prime%20membership%2C%20it%20lacks%20one-day%20delivery%2C%20discounted%20morning%20delivery%2C%20unlimited%20Prime%20Video%20device%20support%2C%20and%204K%20resolution.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Famazon-cuts-price-of-prime-membership-plan-new-pricing-and-benefits%2Farticleshow%2F106157592.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20decided%20not%20to%20tell%20our%20kids%20about%20Santa.%20Here's%20what%20our%20Christmas%20is%20like%20without%20St.%20Nick.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20an%20adult%20guiding%20a%20young%20kid's%20hand%20as%20they%20put%20icing%20on%20gingerbread%20cookies.%20The%20kid%20has%20blonde%20hair%20and%20looks%20down%2C%20smiling.%20They%20are%20wearing%20a%20long-sleeved%20green%20shirt.%20The%20adult%20is%20visible%20from%20the%20arms%20down%20and%20wears%20a%20grey%20and%20white%20striped%20shirt%20and%20red%20and%20white%20striped%20apron.%20To%20their%20left%20is%20a%20paper%20Christmas%20tree%20decoration%20and%20two%20white%20ceramic%20smaller%20Christmas%20trees.%20In%20front%20of%20them%20several%20gingerbread%20cookies%2C%20candy%20canes%2C%20and%20a%20tray%20with%20more%20cookies%20are%20strewn%20across%20the%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656ddcdc7a3c8094d5d91849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuthor%20not%20pictured.%3Cp%3EOlena%20Ivanova%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20my%20daughter%20was%20born%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20decided%20we%20wouldn't%20raise%20our%20kids%20to%20believe%20in%20Santa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20didn't%20want%20Christmas%20to%20be%20all%20about%20gifts%2C%20and%20letting%20her%20sit%20in%20a%20stranger's%20lap%20felt%20wrong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%2C%20we%20bake%20gingerbread%20cookies%2C%20have%20a%20holiday%20photo%20day%2C%20and%20attend%20Christmas%20Eve%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20daughter's%20first%20Christmas%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20made%20a%20big%20decision%3A%20Our%20family%20wasn't%20going%20to%20do%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychotherapist-when-to-tell-child-the-truth-about-santa%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanta%20Claus%3C%2Fa%3E%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20hard%20choice%20for%20me%3A%20When%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20my%20mom%20didn't%20put%20much%20emphasis%20on%20St.%20Nick%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20particularly%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20been%20discussing%20parenting%20priorities%20and%20how%20we%20planned%20to%20raise%20our%20kids%20since%20our%20daughter's%20birth%20%E2%80%94%20weekly%20allowance%3A%20yes%3B%20contact%20sports%3A%20no.%20Call%20me%20a%20%26quot%3BGrinch%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20thought%20some%20of%20the%20Santa%20traditions%20sent%20kids%20the%20wrong%20messages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20our%20daughter%20to%20feel%20secure%20at%20home%2C%20so%20it%20seemed%20counterintuitive%20to%20teach%20her%20that%20a%20strange%20man%20could%20%E2%80%94%20and%20would%20%E2%80%94%20sneak%20in%20through%20the%20chimney%20once%20a%20year.%20Likewise%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20instill%20a%20healthy%20sense%20of%20boundaries%2C%20especially%20with%20strangers%2C%20so%20encouraging%20my%20kid%20to%20sit%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwhy-never-let-child-sit-santas-lap-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20stranger's%20lap%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20mall%20didn't%20seem%20quite%20right%20either.%20Plus%2C%20I%20never%20wanted%20Christmas%20to%20be%20too%20gift-focused%2C%20so%20teaching%20my%20kids%20that%20toys%20were%20free%2C%20ample%2C%20and%20magically%20delivered%20seemed%20to%20miss%20the%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20three%20years%20later%2C%20we%20have%20a%20growing%20toddler%2C%20a%20baby%20girl%2C%20and%20a%20unique%2C%20Santa-free%20holiday%20tradition.%20So%20far%2C%20I'm%20happy%20we've%20stuck%20with%20the%20plan%20%E2%80%94%20but%20bucking%20a%20Christmas%20tradition%20isn't%20always%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it's%20like%20being%20a%20Santa-free%20family%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETalking%20about%20St.%20Nick%20can%20be%20tricky%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20the%20first%20to%20admit%20our%20practice%20can%20make%20the%20holiday%20awkward%20at%20times.%20Unlike%20Jewish%20or%20Muslim%20kids%2C%20my%20girls%20don't%20have%20a%20community%20that%20similarly%20skips%20Santa.%20In%20fact%2C%20my%20in-laws'%20home%20decor%20heavily%20features%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristmas-elf-enchant-holiday-celebration-scottsdale-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhead%20elf%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20this%20time%20of%20year%20and%20he's%20a%20big%20part%20of%20my%20kids'%20and%20their%20cousins'%20lives.%20Father%20Christmas%20even%20visits%20our%20toddler's%20preschool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20assume%20we%20partake%20in%20Santa%20traditions%2C%20so%2C%20when%20other%20adults%20ask%20my%20daughter%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20Santa%20going%20to%20bring%20you%20for%20Christmas%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20must%20explain%20why%20she%20looks%20so%20confused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20also%20getting%20to%20the%20stage%20where%20my%20oldest%20is%20around%20other%20kids%20who%20talk%20about%20St.%20Nick.%20I%20certainly%20don't%20want%20to%20tell%20her%20to%20lie%2C%20but%20I'm%20afraid%20that%20if%20she%20lets%20the%20secret%20slip%2C%20other%20parents%20will%20throw%20candy%20canes%20at%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20fostering%20honesty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20being%20a%20Santa-less%20family%20comes%20with%20some%20awkwardness%2C%20it's%20comforting%20that%20I%20won't%20have%20to%20have%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fkristen-bell-dax-shepard-told-their-kids-the-truth-about-santa-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESanta%20talk%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20my%20kids%20in%20a%20few%20years.%20I%20hate%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20dishonest%20and%20I%20want%20to%20teach%20my%20girls%20to%20trust%20me%20and%20let%20them%20know%20I'll%20always%20tell%20them%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20may%20not%20get%20to%20see%20the%20twinkle%20in%20my%20kids'%20eyes%20when%20they%20talk%20about%20flying%20reindeer%2C%20but%20I%20like%20to%20think%20that%20this%20is%20one%20brick%20in%20a%20foundation%20of%20parental%20trust%20that%20will%20make%20my%20life%20easier%20throughout%20my%20kids'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20Santa-less%20has%20forced%20us%20to%20create%20other%20traditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20don't%20particularly%20miss%20the%20man%20in%20the%20red%20suit%2C%20his%20absence%20does%20leave%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20hole%20in%20our%20winter%20schedule%3A%20We%20aren't%20rushing%20off%20to%20the%20mall%20to%20tell%20Santa%20what%20toys%20we%20want%20and%20we%20don't%20spend%20hours%20writing%20letters%20to%20the%20North%20Pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20free%20time%20has%20forced%20us%20to%20find%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffamily-celebrates-thanksgiving-christmas-birthdays-one-day-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholiday%20traditions%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20be%20intentional%20about%20how%20we%20spend%20the%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20removing%20Santa%20didn't%20take%20away%20from%20the%20religious%20aspects%20of%20the%20holiday%20%E2%80%94%20Christmas%20Eve%20service%20has%20always%20been%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20annual%20traditions%20and%20I%20love%20reading%20our%20Nativity%20storybook%20to%20the%20girls.%20But%20this%20still%20leaves%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20winter%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20some%20of%20our%20favorite%20Santa-free%20traditions%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20instead%20of%20setting%20out%20cookies%20for%20Santa%2C%20we%20make%20gingerbread%20cookies%20from%20scratch.%20We%20always%20create%20a%20gingerbread%20version%20of%20our%20family%20with%20an%20adorable%2C%20edible%20figure%20to%20represent%20each%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20taking%20pictures%20with%20Santa%2C%20we%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftake-nice-family-photos-for-the-holiday-season-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eholiday%20photo%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20we%20meet%20a%20family%20friend%20to%20take%20pictures%2C%20then%20get%20lunch%20at%20our%20favorite%20diner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20reading%20%26quot%3BA%20Visit%20from%20St.%20Nicholas%2C%26quot%3B%20better%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B'Twas%20the%20Night%20Before%20Christmas%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20drink%20hot%20cocoa%20%E2%80%94%20and%20chocolate%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20watch%20what%20I%20consider%20an%20equally%20timeless%20classic%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Muppet%20Christmas%20Carol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20making%20a%20list%20of%20presents%20we%20want%2C%20we%20select%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fgift-cards-charitable-giving-strategy-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echarity%3C%2Fa%3E%20we%20want%20to%20give%20to%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20borrowed%20non-Santa%20traditions%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Icelandic%20tradition%20of%20Jolabokaflod%2C%20where%20we%20give%20each%20other%20a%20new%20book%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20and%20spend%20the%20evening%20reading%20%E2%80%94%20or%20being%20read%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGifts%20aren't%20a%20big%20focus%20but%20they%20still%20pl