%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20together%20make%20up%20for%20around%2065%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20Congress%20has%20lost%204%25%20and%206%25%20of%20its%20votes%20among%20these%20communities%20respectively.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20only%20retained%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20the%20SCs%20at%2033%25%2C%20but%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20the%20OBCs%20has%20risen%20by%207%25%20from%2048%25%20to%2055%25.%20It%20has%20also%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20by%209%25%20from%2030%25%20to%2039%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20among%20STs%20has%20also%20increased%20by%2011%25%20as%20compared%20to%202018%2C%20its%20highest%20increase%20of%20votes%20is%20among%20the%20Muslims.%20In%202018%2C%20only%2052%25%20of%20Muslims%20voted%20for%20Congress%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lokniti.org%2Fstate-election-studies%5C%22%3ECSDS-Lokniti%20Post%20Poll%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20this%20time%20around%2085%25%20of%20Muslims%20voted%20for%20it.%20A%20phenomenal%20increase%20of%20around%2033%25%20of%20Muslim%20votes%20is%20the%20single%20most%20reason%20behind%20the%20Congress%20holding%20on%20to%2040.40%25%20votes%20in%20spite%20of%20its%20loss%20of%20votes%20in%20its%20other%20social%20bases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20population%20of%20the%20MP%20is%20around%206.5%25%20and%20Congress%20might%20have%20reached%20its%20peak%20share%20among%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Among%20many%20other%20things%2C%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20shift%20of%20OBCs%20and%20Adivasis%20towards%20BJP%20is%20the%20vicious%20Hindutva%20campaign%20by%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20its%20organs%20consistently%20throughout%20the%20year%20without%20any%20political%20challenge.%20This%20will%20be%20amplified%20during%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20resulting%20in%20further%20polarisation%20of%20Hindu%20OBCs%20and%20others.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20or%20the%20Congress%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20grassroots%20ideological%20or%20organisational%20counters%20to%20this%20challenge.%20Nor%20do%20they%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20vision%20of%20cultivating%20the%20same%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Congress%20obtained%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2043.04%25%20in%202018%2C%20and%20in%202023%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20its%20humiliating%20defeat%2C%20has%20retained%2042.23%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share.%20Thus%2C%20an%20argument%20is%20being%20made%20that%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20social%20base%20is%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20continues%20to%20have%20a%20good%20social%20base%20among%20the%20SCs%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20which%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20the%20increase%20of%20SC%20votes%20by%206%25%20to%2048%25%20when%20compared%20to%2042%25%20in%202013%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20CSDS%20analysis.%20But%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20STs%2C%20who%20constitute%2032%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20has%20decreased%20by%205%25%2C%20from%2047%20to%2042%25%2C%20and%20among%20OBC%20a%20further%20decrease%20of%203%25%2C%20from%2042%20to%2039%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthree-things-bjps-definitive-victory-in-the-assembly-elections-tells-us%5C%22%3EThree%20Things%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Definitive%20Victory%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Elections%20Tells%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decline%20in%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20among%20Hindus%20in%20the%20state%20is%20majorly%20compensated%20by%2C%20again%2C%20a%20phenomenal%20increase%20of%20Muslim%20votes%20by%2012%25%20(41%25%20to%2053%25).%20Unlike%20MP%2C%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20increased%20its%20vote%20base%20among%20Muslims%20five-fold%2C%20from%20a%20mere%205%25%20to%2027%25.%20Not%20only%20that%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20SCs%20of%20the%20state%20by%2014%25%20%C2%A0(25%25%20to%2039%25)%2C%20among%20the%20STs%20by%2021%25%20(25%25%20to%2046%25)%2C%20and%20among%20OBC%20by%205%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20honour%20of%2040%25%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20majorly%20due%20to%20the%20arithmetic%20increase%20of%20votes%20by%20Muslims.%20Unlike%20MP%2C%20it%20is%20not%20saturated%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20but%20BJP%20itself%20has%20become%20a%20strong%20contender%20for%20Muslim%20votes%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Rajasthan%2C%20Congress%20polled%2039.53%25%20votes%2C%20hardly%201.11%25%20less%20than%20in%202018.%20The%20BJP%20has%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20by%20more%20than%202%25%20to%2041.69%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20what%20the%20CSDS%20survey%20informs%20us%20is%20that%20though%20the%20Congress%20has%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20by%209%25%20(39%25%20to%2048%25)%20among%20SCs%2C%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20STs%20has%20decreased%20by%206%25%20(41%20to%2035%25)%2C%20and%20among%20OBCs%20a%20decrease%20by%203%25.%20(36%20to%2033%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20vote%20share%20could%20sustain%20its%202018%20figure%2C%20majorly%20because%20the%20Muslim%20vote%20share%20increased%20by%20an%20astounding%2028%25%20(62%25%20in%202018%20to%2090%25%20in%202023).%20The%20emergence%20of%20an%20independent%20Adivasi%20party%20has%20cut%20into%20the%20ST%20vote%20share%20of%20both%20BJP%20and%20Congress.%20But%20the%20BJP%20almost%20retained%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20the%20SCs%20at%2033%25%20and%20increased%20its%20vote%20share%20among%20the%20OBC%20by%205%25%2C%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20loss%20of%203%25%20vote%20share%20of%20OBC%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20the%20phenomenal%20increase%20of%20Muslim%20votes%20for%20the%20Congress%20by%2012%25-31%25%20in%20the%20three%20states%20could%20compensate%20for%20its%20loss%20of%20votes%20among%20its%20traditional%20Hindu%20vote%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20survey%20also%20suggests%20that%20among%20the%20Hindus%2C%20especially%20SC%2C%20ST%2C%20and%20OBCs%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20has%20either%20stagnated%20or%20sharply%20decreased.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20increased%20its%20Hindu%20vote%20share%20by%2016%20to%2034%25%20by%20encroaching%20upon%20the%20Congress%20social%20base%20of%20the%20SCs%2C%20STS%2C%20and%20OBCs.%20It%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20depleting%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20smaller%20parties%20in%20the%20fray%2C%20much%20to%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20a%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20replica%20won%E2%80%99t%20help%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20polarisation%20is%20ominous%20for%20the%202024%20elections.%20Even%20among%20the%20rural-urban%2C%20male-female%2C%20and%20other%20class%20categories%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20significant%20inroads%2C%20with%20its%20twin%20agenda%20of%20communal%20polarisation%20and%20last-minute%20personalised%20welfare%20dole-outs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20already%20obvious%20that%20BJP-RSS%20is%20pitching%20on%20issues%20like%20national%20security%2C%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20pride%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%2C%20and%20such%20mythical%20and%20emotive%20agendas%20to%20which%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20counters%20are%20either%20collusive%20or%20complementary%20instead%20of%20confronting%20with%20alternate%20vision%20and%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20electoral%20data%20of%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20has%20many%20political%20and%20ideological%20lessons.%20It%20would%20be%20self-deception%20to%20take%20comfort%20in%20the%20vulnerable%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20dream%20of%20a%20miracle%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20high%20chances%20that%20in%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20fought%20on%20hyper-religious%20nationalism%2C%20the%20very%20same%20Congress%20votes%20may%20shift%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20battle%20of%202024%2C%20therefore%2C%20is%20not%20a%20mathematical%20calculation%20for%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20surely%20cannot%20be%20won%20by%20diluting%20the%20secular%20agenda%20or%20becoming%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20replica.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJP-RSS%20is%20fighting%20an%20ideological%20and%20political%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Republic%2C%20of%20which%20electoral%20victories%20are%20one%20among%20the%20many%20strategies%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20supporters%2C%20cannot%20dream%20of%20saving%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20by%20staging%20an%20unprincipled%20electoral%20battle%20with%20the%20diluted%20versions%20of%20the%20same%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESerious%20politics%20demand%20imagination%20and%20preparation%20beyond%202024%20and%20the%20electoral%20arena%20with%20an%20agenda%20and%20vision%20for%20a%20battle%20for%20substantive%20equality%2C%20social-economic%20justice%20and%20fraternity%2C%20and%20not%20a%20diluted%20version%20of%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fshivasundar%5C%22%3EShivasundar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20activist%20and%20a%20freelance%20journalist%20based%20in%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703073623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06200522%2FF80eu2gWkAATe66.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-take-on-bjp-mere-electoral-battle-not-enough%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20assembly%20election%20results%2C%20many%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20vote%20share%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20intact%20despite%20its%20defeats.%20What%20they%20miss%20is%20the%20steep%20fall%20in%20the%20traditional%20Hindu%20vote%20base%20of%20the%20Congress%20is%20compensated%20by%20an%20increase%20in%20its%20Muslim%20vote%20share.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-take-on-bjp-mere-electoral-battle-not-enough%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22America%20has%20a%20McGonigal%20problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20Charles%20McGonigal%2C%20three%20times%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581daa2cefc010bea250519%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FBI%20chose%20McGonigal%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20top%20grandmasters%20of%20the%20counterintelligence%20game.%20And%20yet%20somehow%2C%20Russian%20associates%20turned%20him%20into%20their%20pawn%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%20%3Cp%3EJohn%20Minchillo%2FAP%3B%20Rachel%20Mendelson%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20of%20Charles%20McGonigal%20is%20bigger%20than%20one%20corrupt%20FBI%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it's%20bigger%20than%20the%20entire%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20case%20against%20Charles%20McGonigal%2C%20the%20FBI's%20former%20New%20York%20counterintelligence%20chief%20%E2%80%94%20a%20scandal%20that%20launched%20a%20thousand%20conspiracy%20theories%20%E2%80%94%20is%20beginning%20to%20wind%20down.%20Last%20week%2C%20a%20judge%20in%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20sentenced%20McGonigal%20to%2050%20months%20in%20prison%3B%20a%20second%20judge%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20sentence%20McGonigal%20on%20a%20different%20set%20of%20charges%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20bigger%20story%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0about%20transnational%20flows%20of%20money%2C%20intelligence%2C%20and%20influence%2C%20and%20the%20weakness%20of%20the%20legal%20and%20ethical%20firewalls%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20constrain%20them%20%E2%80%94%20is%20just%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20McGonigal%20indictments%20offer%20a%20rare%20glimpse%20of%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20the%20Acela%20corridor%2C%20a%20global%20bazaar%20where%20contacts%2C%20secrets%2C%20and%20influence%20are%20swapped%20for%20millions%20while%20the%20laws%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20protect%20US%20national%20security%20interests%20are%20often%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20with%20McGonigal's%20two%20guilty%20pleas%20and%20first%20sentencing%2C%20that%20rare%20window%20into%20how%20things%20really%20work%20inside%20the%20steakhouses%20of%20Washington%20and%20Manhattan%20is%20closing.%20McGonigal%20was%20embraced%20by%20this%20clubby%20world%20of%20lobbyists%20and%20law%20enforcement%20dons%20even%20as%20he%20brought%20home%20bags%20of%20cash%20to%20fund%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharles-mcgonigal-fbi-indictment-allison-guerriero-russia-deripaska-spies-nypd-giuliani-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecret%20double%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20of%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexclusive-fbi-charles-mcgonigal-trump-russia-grand-jury-oleg-deripaska-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBI%20was%20first%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20break%20the%20news%20that%20prosecutors%20were%20scrutinizing%20McGonigal's%20contacts%20with%20Albanian%20officials%20and%20a%20powerful%20Russian%20oligarch.%20When%20McGonigal%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20in%20January%2C%20the%20media%20and%20Capitol%20Hill%20reacted%20with%20shock.%20How%20could%20one%20of%20the%20FBI's%20senior-most%20counter-intelligence%20officials%20retire%20and%20then%20illegally%20take%20money%20from%20a%20sanctioned%20Russian%20oligarch%20he%20had%20been%20investigating%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20was%20before%20Robert%20Menendez%2C%20who%20is%20still%20a%20sitting%20Democratic%20senator%20from%20New%20Jersey%2C%20was%20indicted%20for%20allegedly%20accepting%20gold%20bars%20and%20bundles%20of%20cash%20so%20that%20military%20aid%20could%20keep%20flowing%20to%20the%20Egypt's%20authoritarian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20before%20FBI%20agents%20seized%20the%20phones%20of%20Eric%20Adams%2C%20who%20is%20still%20the%20mayor%20of%20New%20York%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20probe%20into%20campaign%20donations%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Turkey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20McGonigal's%20corruption%20was%20surprising%20then%2C%20it%20should%20be%20less%20surprising%20now.%20Official%20corruption%20in%20America%20goes%20beyond%20one%20agency%2C%20one%20administration%2C%20or%20one%20political%20party.%20It%20isn't%20political.%20It's%20cultural%2C%20the%20product%20of%20a%20society%20so%20obsessed%20with%20wealth%20that%20even%20its%20best-compensated%20public%20officials%20see%20themselves%20as%20middle-class%20strivers.%20Despite%20%24850%2C000%20in%20income%20and%20%241.5%20million%20in%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20his%20pre-sentencing%20report%2C%20McGonigal's%20attorneys%20tried%20to%20excuse%20his%20behavior%20by%20saying%20that%20he%20needed%20%26quot%3Bto%20find%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20a%20living.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20high%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20lead%20attorney%2C%20Seth%20DuCharme%2C%20argued%20in%20a%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20prestige%2C%20and%20he%20has%20respect%2C%20but%20he's%20not%20a%20billionaire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOleg%20Deripaska%2C%20the%20Russian%20oligarch%20who%20hired%20McGonigal%2C%20is%20a%20billionaire%2C%20one%20with%20longstanding%20ties%20to%20Vladimir%20Putin%20and%20whose%20alleged%20involvement%20with%20bribery%2C%20murder%2C%20and%20organized%20crime%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome.treasury.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fsm0338%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20cited%20by%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department.%20(Deripaska%20has%20denied%20all%20wrongdoing%2C%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Fderipaska-oligarch-ukraine-russia-war%2F31734624.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicly%20distanced%3C%2Fa%3E%20himself%20from%20Putin%20since%20the%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20illegality%20of%20McGonigal%20taking%20Deripaska's%20money%20in%20violation%20of%20US%20sanctions%2C%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20Hagan%20Scotten%20made%20clear%20in%20court%20why%20their%20relationship%20should%20be%20so%20worrying.%20Pushing%20back%20on%20an%20argument%20by%20McGonigal's%20attorneys%20that%20his%20crime%20was%20less%20serious%20than%20transferring%20military%20equipment%2C%20Scotten%20asked%20the%20judge%20to%20consider%20the%20value%20to%20the%20Kremlin%20of%20%26quot%3Bhaving%20a%20former%20counter-intelligence%20chief%20on%20their%20payroll.%20What%20is%20more%20valuable%20to%20them%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20would%20Putin%20ask%20his%20oligarchs%20to%20pay%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20Scotten%20went%20on.%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20would%20%3Cem%3Ethat%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20been%20worth%20to%20him%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20has%20never%20alleged%20that%20McGonigal%20was%20spying%20for%20Russia%2C%20Scotten%20believed%20that's%20where%20things%20were%20likely%20headed.%20McGonigal%20%26quot%3Bcannot%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20that%20he%20was%20selling%20his%20service%20to%20a%20scoundrel%20working%20against%20America's%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20New%20York%20prosecutors%20wrote%20in%20their%20filing%20on%20his%20sentencing.%20%26quot%3BThe%20investigative%20skills%2C%20contacts%2C%20and%20influence%20of%20a%20former%20senior%20American%20counterintelligence%20officer%20are%20of%20obvious%2C%20and%20dangerous%2C%20value%20to%20an%20agent%20of%20Vladimir%20Putin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20McGonigal%20story%2C%20as%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20government's%20filings%20and%20BI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffbi-charlie-mcgonigal-labyrinth-oleg-deripaska-russia-trump-allison-guerriero-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reads%20like%20the%20opening%20chapters%20of%20a%20classic%20spy%20novel%3A%20Operatives%20spot%20and%20then%20recruit%20a%20hapless%20minion%20and%20set%20about%20gradually%20turning%20his%20loyalties%20around%20to%20align%20with%20theirs.%20McGonigal%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20FBI's%20top%20grandmasters%20at%20this%20game%2C%20and%20what%20might%20be%20most%20astonishing%20about%20the%20allegations%20is%20the%20degree%20to%20which%20he%20apparently%20allowed%20his%20Russian%20associates%20to%20remake%20him%20into%20their%20pawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20still%20working%20at%20the%20FBI%2C%20McGonigal%20was%20introduced%20by%20one%20former%20Russian%20diplomat%20to%20another%2C%20more%20senior%20one%2C%20with%20rumored%20ties%20to%20Russian%20intelligence%20who%20worked%20with%20Deripaska.%20He%20was%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government%2C%20asked%20to%20do%20something%20simple%20but%20also%2C%20arguably%2C%20slightly%20compromising%20%E2%80%94%20arrange%20for%20the%20second%20diplomat's%20daughter%20to%20receive%20VIP%20treatment%20from%20the%20New%20York%20City%20Police%20Department.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20after%20McGonigal's%20retirement%2C%20he%20met%20with%20Deripaska%20at%20two%20of%20his%20residences%2C%20in%20London%20and%20Vienna.%20And%20then%20he%20started%20accepting%20Deripaska's%20money%2C%20surreptitiously.%20It%20flowed%20from%20a%20Russian%20bank%20to%20one%20shell%20company%20based%20in%20Cyprus%20to%20another%20controlled%20by%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20Jennifer%20H.%20Rearden%20appeared%20to%20find%20Scotten's%20argument%20compelling.%20Last%20week%2C%20she%20sentenced%20McGonigal%20to%2050%20months%20in%20prison%2C%203%20years%20probation%2C%20and%20a%20%2440%2C000%20fine.%20McGonigal's%20lawyers%2C%20citing%20his%20record%20of%20service%20within%20the%20FBI%2C%20had%20asked%20the%20judge%20for%20no%20additional%20confinement.%20Rearden%20ordered%20McGonigal%20to%20turn%20himself%20in%20on%20February%2026.%20He%20will%20be%20sentenced%20in%20a%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20district%20court%20under%20a%20second%20plea%20agreement%20on%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20New%20York%2C%20prosecutors%20said%2C%20McGonigal%20continued%20to%20wield%20the%20privileges%20and%20leverage%20the%20contacts%20that%20he'd%20enjoyed%20as%20the%20FBI's%20New%20York%20City%20counter-intelligence%20chief%2C%20even%20though%20he%20no%20longer%20held%20that%20job.%20He%20traveled%20the%20world%20for%20meetings%20with%20foreign%20ministers%2C%20heads%20of%20state%2C%20and%20titans%20of%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%20London%20get-together%20with%20Deripaska%20that%20was%20so%20alarming%20to%20British%20intelligence%20agents%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbritish-uk-london-deripaska-charles-mcgonigal-fbi-meeting-russia-surveillance-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20alerted%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20US%20counterparts.%20And%20back%20in%20New%20York%2C%20according%20to%20prosecutors%2C%20McGonigal%20continued%20to%20put%20an%20FBI%20placard%20on%20the%20windshield%20of%20his%20car%2C%20so%20he%20could%20park%20wherever%20he%20pleased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20who%20the%20FBI%20chose%20to%20promote%20to%20one%20of%20its%20most%20senior%20positions%20and%20entrust%20with%20its%20most%20sensitive%20secrets.%20In%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dgw7960b5518%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20testimony%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Committee%2C%20FBI%20Director%20Christopher%20Wray%20said%20the%20Justice%20Department's%20inspector%20general%20is%20%26quot%3Bengaged%26quot%3B%20in%20scrutinizing%20the%20McGonigal%20matter.%20Members%20of%20Congress%20from%20both%20parties%20have%20also%20demanded%20answers%20of%20the%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20McGonigal's%20two%20plea%20agreements%20mean%20there%20is%20likely%20a%20lot%20about%20his%20career%20that%20may%20never%20be%20made%20public.%20These%20include%20his%20alleged%20attempts%20(after%20retiring)%20to%20get%20paid%20for%20arranging%20meetings%20with%20UN%20officials%2C%20and%20his%20role%20in%20the%20Trump-Russia%20investigation%2C%20and%20his%20time%20in%20the%20FBI's%20New%20York%20Field%20Office%20during%20the%20crucial%20months%20just%20before%20the%202016%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20get%20caught%20up%20in%20their%20Bond%20fantasies%2C%20their%20addiction%20to%20money%2C%20and%20their%20need%20to%20maintain%20their%20indispensability%20by%20offering%20more%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20one%20Washington%20insider%20familiar%20with%20the%20intelligence%20world.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20small%20step%20from%20selling%20services%20to%20foreign%20oligarchs%20to%20acting%20as%20the%20agent%20of%20a%20foreign%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20foreign%20oligarchs%20remain%20among%20the%20core%20clientele%20of%20otherwise%20respectable%20lawyers%2C%20lobbyists%2C%20and%20former%20US%20officials.%20McGonigal%20is%20not%20the%20end%20of%20this%20story%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20a%20warning.%20The%20US%20should%20be%20most%20worried%20about%20those%20who%20are%20still%20getting%20away%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMattathias%20Schwartz%20is%20chief%20national%20security%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20schwartz79%40protonmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-charles-mcgonigal-problem-russia-kremlin-deripaska-fbi-sentencing-corruption-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703073601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63dc17c60a08ae0018a68a65%