amp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fawards%2Fbafta-film-awards-rules-2025-theatrical-eligibility-1235847049%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Parliament%20Impasse%20-%20And%20The%20Loser%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20fierce%20showdown%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition%2C%20142%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%20from%20parliament.%20On%20December%2018%2C%2078%20MPs%20-%2033%20from%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%2045%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha%20-%20were%20suspended.%20A%20day%20later%2C%2050%20more%20MPs%20were%20suspended%2C%20which%20left%20the%20Opposition%20benches%20nearly%20empty%20in%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20session%20of%20parliament.%20The%20suspended%20members%20were%20protesting%20against%20the%20parliament%20security%20breach%20of%20December%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20142%20suspended%20MPs%20are%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20history%20of%20parliament.%20The%20Opposition%20in%20both%20Houses%20has%20been%20demanding%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20statement%20on%20the%20security%20breach%2C%20in%20which%20two%20men%20broke%20into%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20set%20off%20smoke%20canisters%20and%20a%20woman%20and%20a%20man%20did%20the%20same%20outside%20parliament.%20A%20majority%20of%20the%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%20for%20the%20entire%20winter%20session%2C%20which%20ends%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20maintained%20that%20security%20in%20the%20parliament%20complex%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20secretariat%20and%20it%20can%20only%20follow%20the%20Speaker's%20orders%20on%20the%20subject.%20Also%2C%20similar%20breaches%20have%20happened%20in%20the%20past%20and%20the%20Opposition%20is%20merely%20politicising%20the%20issue%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Speaker%20of%20the%20House%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Secretary%20Home%20and%20has%20instructed%20me%20to%20get%20a%20high-level%20inquiry%20(on%20security%20beach)%20done.%20To%20increase%20the%20security%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%2C%20a%20committee%20has%20also%20been%20constituted%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20DG%20CRPF.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20an%20investigation%20going%20on%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Opposition%20does%20not%20want%20the%20House%20to%20function...%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20saying%20that%20unemployment%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20all%20this%20took%20place.%20Does%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20support%20all%20this%3F%20What%20irresponsible%20statement%20is%20this%3F%20They%20(the%20Opposition)%20want%20to%20do%20politics%20in%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20accuse%20the%20government%20of%20browbeating%20the%20Opposition%20and%20trying%20to%20muzzle%20the%20voice%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20attack%20in%20parliament.%20It%20was%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20security%20of%20the%20members.%20The%20Opposition%20members%20are%20merely%20demanding%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Home%20Minister%20speak%20in%20parliament%20instead%20of%20speaking%20outside%20on%20it.%20It%20is%20a%20mockery%20of%20democracy.%20When%20parliament%20is%20in%20session%2C%20it%20is%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%20and%20against%20parliamentary%20conventions%20to%20give%20statements%20outside%20the%20House%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Rajeev%20Gowda%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20also%20feels%20that%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20government's%20strategy%20to%20pass%20crucial%20legislation%20without%20debate%2C%20in%20the%20same%20way%20it%20has%20underutilised%20the%20workings%20of%20standing%20and%20parliamentary%20committees.%20Important%20bills%20are%20pending%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20These%20include%20three%20bills%20to%20replace%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20and%20draft%20legislation%20to%20set%20up%20a%20mechanism%20to%20appoint%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20and%20Election%20Commissioners.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20needs%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20Opposition%20and%20find%20a%20solution%20as%20running%20the%20House%20is%20its%20responsibility.%20The%20government%20wants%20to%20pass%20bills%20without%20any%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20Opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Mr%20Gowda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20mass%20suspensions%20in%20the%20past%20but%20this%20is%20a%20record%20high.%20On%2015%20March%201989%2C%2063%20members%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20were%20suspended%20in%20a%20row%20over%20the%20Justice%20MP%20Thakkar%20Committee%20report%20on%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination.%20In%202019%2C%20then%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Sumitra%20Mahajan%20suspended%2045%20opposition%20MPs%20for%20disrupting%20House%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20week's%20suspensions%20have%20slashed%20the%20Opposition%20strength%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20almost%20half.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%2095%20MPs%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20of%20which%2045%20are%20suspended.%20In%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20has%20lost%20a%20third%20of%20its%20members%20-%2046%20of%20133%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20government%20doesn't%20want%20to%20hear%20any%20Opposition%20voice%20in%20parliament.%20Suspension%20and%20dismissal%20are%20used%20as%20tools%20to%20attain%20that%20objective.%20Parliament%20has%20never%20seen%20such%20blatant%20use%20of%20power%20against%20an%20elected%20opposition.%20This%20is%20unfortunate%20for%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Nawal%20Kishore%2C%20RJD%20national%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20suspending%20MPs%2C%20the%20government%20is%20denying%20people%20their%20representation%20in%20parliament%20during%20important%20business.%20The%20government%20took%20up%20bills%20as%20opposition%20MPs%20relentlessly%20shouted%20slogans.%20Important%20bills%20like%20one%20providing%20for%2033%20per%20cent%20quota%20for%20women%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Puducherry%20Assemblies%20were%20passed%20within%20minutes%20on%20December%2018%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20So%20was%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20(Second%20Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20government%20passed%20the%20Post%20Office%20Bill%2C%202023%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20national%20security%20and%20also%20introduced%20the%20Telecommunications%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20the%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20in%20such%20a%20large%20number%20is%20a%20grave%20issue%2C%20I%20think%20harping%20on%20one%20issue%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20other%20important%20business%20of%20the%20House%20is%20not%20responsible%20behaviour%2C%20considering%20so%20many%20important%20bills%20are%20to%20be%20tabled%2C%20which%20require%20serious%20deliberation%20by%20all%20members.%20Some%20restraint%20on%20the%20part%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%20is%20called%20for%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ashok%20Acharya%20Professor%2C%20Department%20of%20Political%20Science%2C%20University%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20have%20taken%20extreme%20positions.%20The%20loss%20of%20time%20-%20intangible%20-%20and%20the%20loss%20of%20public%20money%20-%20tangible%20-%20is%20immeasurable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703073540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fksguhv28_opposition-mps-suspended-_625x300_19_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-parliament-impasse-and-the-loser-is-4709956%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20fierce%20sho