0muscle%20and%20burn%20fat%20for%20the%20bodybuilding%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20started%20bodybuilding%20as%20young%20adult%20with%20'no%20idea'%20what%20he%20was%20doing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Jones%20didn't%20hit%20the%20bodybuilding%20stage%20as%20a%20teen%2C%20it%20wasn't%20for%20lack%20of%20trying.%20Coming%20from%20an%20athletic%20background%2C%20he%20said%20he%20did%20his%20best%20to%20get%20in%20shape%20using%20the%20advice%20he%20could%20find%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20social%20media%2C%20I%20just%20read%20magazines%20and%20stuff%2C%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20ate%20a%20can%20of%20tuna%20for%20breakfast.%20I%20ate%20a%20can%20of%20tuna%20for%20lunch%2C%20with%20maybe%20or%20maybe%20not%20some%20rice.%20And%20I%20ate%20a%20can%20of%20tuna%20for%20dinner.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20got%20back%20in%20shape%20following%20a%2026-year%20break%20from%20the%20gym%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20minimal%20guidance%2C%20Jones%20said%20it%20wasn't%20hard%20for%20him%20to%20fall%20off%20the%20fitness%20habit%20as%20he%20started%20a%20career%2C%20got%20married%2C%20and%20had%20kids%2C%20prompting%20a%20nearly%20three-decade%20break.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20rested%20up%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20he%20began%20to%20put%20on%20weight%20due%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20shift%20work%2C%20high%20stress%2C%20and%20the%20influence%20of%20coworkers%20also%20trying%20to%20manage%20the%20pressure%20with%20food%20and%20drink.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20get%20in%20a%20drinking%20circle%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20you're%20in%20a%20barbecue%20cookoff%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20take%20long.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20fitness%20dreams%20were%20deferred%2C%20not%20forgotten%20entirely.%20Jones%20said%20that%20several%20years%20before%20retirement%2C%20he%20decided%20he%20would%20use%20the%20reprieve%20from%20work%20to%20lose%20weight%20and%20get%20back%20in%20shape.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20Jones%20had%20dropped%20about%2080%20pounds%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwalking-10000-steps-for-health-not-science-based-in-marketing-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalking%20regularly%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20he%20ate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Athlete%20Ken%20Jones%20smiling%20onstage%20as%20he%20holds%20a%20pair%20of%20pants%20that%20used%20to%20fit%20him%20before%20he%20lost%20more%20than%20100%20pounds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6580bf021c5c7b8c9a097d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKen%20Jones%20lost%20nearly%20half%20his%20body%20weight%20after%20retirement%20thanks%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20walking%2C%20tracking%20his%20macronutrients%20with%20the%20MyFitnessPal%20app%2C%20and%20consistent%20gym%20sessions.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20Natural%20Fit%20Federation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20a%20bodybuilding%20win%2C%20his%20next%20goal%20is%20to%20go%20pro%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20stage%20in%20Jones'%20emerging%20fitness%20transformation%20came%20as%20he%20was%20working%20part-time%20at%20a%20local%20college%2C%20and%20connected%20with%20a%20student%20who%20was%20interested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-build-muscle-according-to-pro-bodybuilder-sadik-hadzovic-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebodybuilding%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Jones%20said%20he%20asked%20for%20nutrition%20advice%20and%20then%20started%20training%20with%20the%20man%2C%20who%20was%20about%2015%20years%20younger%20and%20preparing%20for%20a%20physique%20c