on%20but%20this%20is%20what%20happened%20yesterday%20%26amp%3B%20it's%20devious.%20I%20asked%20%40PiyushGoyal%20why%20the%20small%20bunch%20of%20us%20remaining%20INDIA%20MPs%20weren't%20being%20suspended%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20despite%20protesting%20in%20the%20well.%20Because%2046%20of%20our%20INDIA%20colleagues%20got%20instantly%20suspended%20for%20the%20same%20thing%20a%20day%20earlier.%20He%20says%20'Because%20if%20there's%20zero%20Opposition%20MPs%20left%2C%20it%20looks%20bad%20for%20us'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%20he%20added%20-%20%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%2C%20you'll%20all%20be%20suspended%20before%20%40AmitShah%20ji%20comes%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20to%20table%20the%20criminal%20law%20Bills%26quot%3B.%20This%20is%20what%20our%20Parliament%20has%20now%20become%20reduced%20to%20under%20Modi's%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gokhale%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOnce%20again%2C%20a%20false%2C%20mischievous%20piece%20of%20fake%20news%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20that%20is%20now%20the%20standard%20operating%20manual%20of%20the%20Congress%20led%20Ghamandia%20Gatbandhan.%20It%20comes%20soon%20after%20an%20unprecedented%20insult%20of%20the%20Hon'ble%20Vice%20President%20of%20India%20by%20Congress%20leader%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiyushGoyal%2Fstatus%2F1737376341912129819%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrashing%20the%20Trinamool%20MP's%20claim%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bfalse%2C%20mischievous%20piece%20of%20fake%20news%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20again%2C%20a%20false%2C%20mischievous%20piece%20of%20fake%20news%20by%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Saket%20Gokhale%20that%20is%20now%20the%20standard%20