rt%20ban%20on%20the%20vegetable%20in%20India%2C%20questions%20have%20been%20raised%20on%20if%20India%20is%20losing%20an%20established%20international%20market%20for%20its%20produce%20as%20Nepal%20and%20others%20begin%20assessing%20alternatives%20to%20the%20Indian%20onion.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20farmers%20who%20grew%20the%20crop%20expecting%20profits%20are%20consumed%20with%20worry%20due%20to%20falling%20domestic%20prices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20introduced%20a%20minimum%20export%20price%20of%20%24800%20per%20tonne%20on%20onion%20exports%20on%20October%2028%20this%20year.%20On%20December%208%2C%20the%20curbs%20on%20onion%20export%20were%20extended%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20total%20ban%20until%20March%2031%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20sweeping%20export%20ban%2C%20people%20in%20Nepal%20are%20grappling%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20the%20kitchen%20staple.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nepal%20government%20has%20announced%20its%20decision%20to%20formally%20request%20India%20to%20send%20onions%20to%20address%20the%20scarcity%20that%20has%20affected%20markets%20in%20the%20country%20after%20onion%20importers%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20a%20potential%20shortage%20of%20the%20vegetable%20in%20Nepal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20the%20request%20by%20onion%20traders%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20request%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20send%20onion%20to%20Nepal.%20We%20will%20send%20the%20request%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20official%20in%20Nepal%E2%80%99s%20industry%20ministry%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2023%2F12%2F18%2Fnepal-to-request-india-for-onion-supply%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EKathmandu%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENepal%20relies%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20India%20for%20all%20of%20its%20onion%20imports.%20Any%20ripples%20in%20onion%20supply%20from%20India%20have%20an%20amplified%20impact%20on%20Nepali%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-onion-export-ban-hits-neighbouring-countries-steep-price-hikes-reported%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Onion%20Export%20Ban%20Hits%20Neighbouring%20Countries%2C%20Steep%20Price%20Hikes%20Reported%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELosing%20international%20market%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20directive%2C%20the%20export%20of%20onions%20may%20be%20allowed%20based%20on%20permission%20granted%20by%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20other%20countries%20based%20on%20the%20request%20of%20their%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Nepali%20officials%20are%20also%20in%20discussions%20with%20onion%20importers%20to%20potentially%20source%20the%20vegetable%20from%20other%20countries%20like%20Pakistan%20and%20China.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImporting%20large%20quantities%20of%20onion%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20other%20than%20India%2C%20is%20not%20possible%20because%20it%20is%20a%20perishable%20commodity%2C%20said%20the%20government%20officials.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20no%20government%20bodies%20import%20onions%2C%20our%20role%20is%20to%20facilitate%20the%20importers%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkathmandupost.com%2Fmoney%2F2023%2F12%2F18%2Fnepal-to-request-india-for-onion-supply%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20if%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20get%20the%20approval%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20we%20have%20an%20option%20to%20import%20from%20third%20countries%2C%20including%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%2C%20Nepal%20imported%20around%20190%20tonnes%20of%20onions%20worth%20Rs%206.75%20billion%20from%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ban%20has%20also%20led%20to%20onion%20smuggling%20across%20the%20porous%20borders%20with%20law%20enforcement%20seizing%20illegally%20imported%20onions%20on%20several%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDomestic%20impact%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20export%20ban%20has%20not%20only%20affected%20the%20price%20of%20onions%20internationally%2C%20but%20has%20also%20caused%20a%20price%20drop%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%20affecting%20farmer%20incomes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHundreds%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fnashik%2Fonion-farmers-protest-on-mumbai-agra-highway-over-centres-ban-on-exports%2Farticleshow%2F105837748.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20onion%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Nashik%20district%20blocked%20the%20Mumbai-Agra%20Highway%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20three%20locations%20last%20week%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20ban%20the%20export%20of%20onions%2C%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOngoing%20protests%20at%20onion%20markets%20in%20Lasalgaon%2C%20Nandgaon%2C%20Pimpalgaon%2C%20and%20Umarane%20in%20Nashik%20had%20led%20to%20temporary%20closure%20of%20operations%20in%20these%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20imposition%20of%20MEP%20in%20October%2C%20the%20average%20wholesale%20prices%20of%20onions%20had%20dropped%20by%2024%25%20in%20the%20first%20five%20days%20to%20Rs%203%2C650%20per%20quintal%20at%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20wholesale%20onion%20market%20at%20Lasalgaon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20chief%20minis