aapsee%20Pannu%2C%20Vikrant%20Massey%2C%20Sunny%20Kaushal%2C%20and%20director%20Jayprad%20Desai.%20Fans%20flooded%20the%20comments%20section%20with%20excitement%2C%20eagerly%20anticipating%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20release.Phir%20Aayi%20Hasseen%20Dillruba%20follows%20the%20success%20of%20its%20predecessor%2C%20Haseen%20Dillruba%2C%20released%20in%202021%20and%20directed%20by%20Vinil%20Mathew.%20The%20psychological%20thriller%2C%20starring%20Taapsee%20Pannu%20and%20Vikrant%20Massey%2C%20centers%20around%20a%20woman%20accused%20of%20plotting%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20murder%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Finside-the-wrapping-up-of-phir-aayi-hasseen-dillrubas-shoot-with-taapsee-pannu-vikrant-massey-and-sunny-kaushal-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F106154643.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KSA%20Visa%3A%20New%20Saudi%20Arabia%20Platform%20To%20Benefit%20Hajj%20Pilgrims%20From%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20has%20launched%20a%20unified%20national%20platform%20for%20visa%20applications%2C%20called%20KSA%20Visa.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.com%2Fnode%2F2428686%2Fsaudi-arabia%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArab%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20system%20connects%20more%20than%2030%20ministries%2C%20authorities%20and%20private-sector%20organizations%20to%20streamline%20the%20process%20of%20applying%20for%20visas%20for%20Hajj%2C%20Umrah%2C%20tourism%2C%20business-related%20visits%2C%20and%20employment.%20This%20comes%20weeks%20after%20Saudi%20Minister%20of%20Hajj%20and%20Umrah%20Tawfig%20bin%20Fawzan%20Al-Rabiah's%20visit%20to%20India.%20The%20move%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20Hajj%20pilgrims%20from%20India.%20A%20local%20outlet%20claimed%20that%2020%20lakh%20Indian%20pilgrims%20are%20expected%20to%20visit%20Saudi%20Arabia%20for%20Hajj%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKSA%20Visa%20makes%20use%20of%20the%20latest%20technology%2C%20especially%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20to%20help%20users%20identify%20available%20visas.%20The%20centralised%20system%20of%20the%20smart%20search%20engine%20will%20provide%20detailed%20guidance%20on%20visa%20requirements%20and%20application%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20platform%20was%20launched%20at%20the%20digital%20government%20forum%20in%20Riyadh%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20move%20is%20part%20of%20the%20emirate's%20ambitious%20goal%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20tourists%20and%20raising%20the%20target%20to%20150%20million%20visits%20annually%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsaudigazette.com.sa%2Farticle%2F638836%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESaudi%20Gazette%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20the%20country%20has%20issued%20more%20than%2018.6%20million%20visas%20during%20the%20year%202023%2C%20and%20it%20reduced%20the%20duration%20for%20issuing%20digital%20visas%20to%2060%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20system%20specifically%20designed%20to%20provide%20pilgrims%20from%20India%20with%20enhanced%20flexibility%20throughout%20their%20journey%2C%20particularly%20women%20who%20go%20on%20solo%20Umrah%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20steps%2C%20visa%20for%20Umrah%20has%20been%20extended%20to%2090%20days%2C%20and%20the%20country%20has%20also%20introduced%20a%20four-day%20transit%20visa%20to%20accommodate%20the%20growing%20influx%20of%20Indian%20pilgrims%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Saudi%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20promoting%20gender%20equality%20and%20cultivating%20a%20safer%2C%20more%20embracing%20environment%2C%20these%20changes%20collectively%20aim%20to%20ensure%20a%20more%20fulfilling%20and%20secure%20pilgrimage%20experience%20for%20all%20travellers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Al-Rabiah%20said%20he%20expects%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20Umrah%20pilgrims%20in%20the%20near%20future%20in%20view%20of%20the%20impactful%20initiatives%20introduced%20to%20enhance%20experiences%20of%20the%20pilgrims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20initiatives%20are%20designed%20to%20create%20a%20seamless%20and%20inviting%20environment%20for%20all%20individuals%20embarking%20on%20a%20spiritual%20pilgrimage%20to%20the%20Two%20Holy%20Mosques%20and%20exploring%20the%20rich%20historical%20and%20cultural%20heritage%20of%20Islamic%20sites%20and%20diverse%20tourist%20attractions%20within%20the%20Kingdom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20an%20estimated%20quota%20of%201%2C75%2C025%20for%20Indian%20pilgrims%20for%20the%20Hajj%20season%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703069700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-10%2Fsaudi-arabia-visa_650x400_41477028514.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-launches-unified-visa-platform-ksa-visa-indian-hajj-pilgrims-to-benefit-4709567%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Saudi%20move%20is%20part%20of%20the%20emirate's%20ambitious%20goal%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20tourists%20and%20raising%20the%20target%20to%20150%20million%20visits%20annually%20by%202030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-launches-unified-visa-platform-ksa-visa-indian-hajj-pilgrims-to-benefit-4709567%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-launches-unified-visa-platform-ksa-visa-indian-hajj-pilgrims-to-benefit-4709567%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsaudi-arabia-launches-unified-visa-platform-ksa-visa-indian-hajj-pilgrims-to-benefit-4709567%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title