47.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2221%20Cases%20Of%20New%20Covid%20Variant%20JN.1%20In%20India%20Confirmed%20In%20Lab%20Tests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20so%20far%20reported%2021%20cases%20of%20the%20new%20coronavirus%20variant%20JN.1%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20government%20think%20tank%20NITI%20Aayog%20member%20(Health)%20VK%20Paul%20said%20today.%20Goa%20has%20reported%2019%20cases%20of%20the%20JN.1%20variant%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%20and%20Kerala%20one%20each%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20today%20reviewed%20the%20COVID-19%20situation%20and%20preparedness%20of%20public%20health%20systems%20in%20view%20of%20rising%20Covid%20cases%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20to%20be%20on%20alert%20and%20be%20prepared%20against%20new%20and%20emerging%20strains%20of%20the%20coronavirus%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mandaviya%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20Ministry%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20for%20smooth%20coordination%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20states%20to%20ensure%20efficient%20management%20of%20Covid.%20%26quot%3BLet%20us%20undertake%20mock%20drills%20once%20every%20three%20months%20at%20both%20the%20central%20and%20state%20levels%20and%20share%20best%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Health%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Minister%20reminded%20the%20states%20that%20Covid%20is%20not%20over%20yet%2C%20so%20it%20is%20essential%20for%20the%20states%20to%20monitor%20emerging%20evidences%20of%20Covid%20cases%2C%20symptoms%2C%20and%20case%20severity%20to%20plan%20appropriate%20public%20health%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealth%20Ministry%20secretary%20Sudhansh%20Pant%20in%20a%20presentation%20on%20the%20global%20and%20domestic%20Covid%20situation%20said%20cases%20in%20India%20are%20significantly%20less%20compared%20to%20the%20global%20numbers.%20But%20in%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20steep%20rise%20in%20active%20cases%20from%20115%20on%20December%206%20to%20614%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%2C%2092.8%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20cases%20are%20home-isolation%2C%20indicating%20mild%20illness%2C%20and%20no%20increase%20in%20hospitalisation%20rates%20have%20been%20seen%20due%20to%20Covid%2C%20Mr%20Pant%20said%20during%20the%20presentation.%20The%20cases%20that%20are%20hospitalised%20are%20due%20to%20other%20medical%20conditions%2C%20while%20Covid%20is%20an%20incidental%20finding%2C%20the%20Health%20Secretary%20said%2C%20adding%20a%20rise%20in%20daily%20positivity%20rate%20has%20been%20observed%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%20Positivity%20rate%20is%20the%20number%20of%20confirmed%20cases%20per%20100%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pant%20said%20the%20JN.1%20variant%20is%20under%20intense%20scientific%20scrutiny%20but%20not%20a%20cause%20of%20immediate%20concern.%20No%20clustering%20of%20cases%20due%20to%20the%20JN.1%20variant%20has%20been%20observed%20in%20India.%20All%20the%20cases%20were%20found%20to%20be%20mild%2C%20and%20the%20patients%20recovered%20without%20any%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703069100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fr935u0bo_covid-generic-1200-_625x300_08_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F21-cases-of-new-covid-variant-jn-1-in-india-confirmed-in-lab-tests-4709352%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20so%20far%20reported%2021%20cases%20of%20the%20new%20coronavirus%20variant%20JN.1%20from%20across%20the%20country%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F21-cases-of-new-covid-variant-jn-1-in-india-confirmed-in-lab-tests-4709352%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw