ter%20an%20extensive%20search.%20Mr%20Olver%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20his%20trawling%20net%20snagged%20what%20he%20believed%20was%20a%20wing%20of%20the%20commercial%20plane%20just%20six%20months%20after%20it%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hasn't%20spoken%20about%20it%20for%20years.%20But%20now%2C%20the%2077-year-old%20wants%20the%20world%20to%20hear%20his%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20bloody%20great%20wing%20of%20a%20big%20jet%20airliner%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Olver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20questioned%20myself%3B%20I've%20looked%20for%20a%20way%20out%20of%20this.%20I%20wish%20to%20Christ%20I'd%20never%20seen%20the%20thing...%20but%20there%20it%20is.%20It%20was%20a%20jet's%20wing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fisherman%20said%20the%20wing%20was%20bigger%20than%20a%20private%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Olver%20said%20the%20note%20of%20his%20trawler's%20engine%20deepened%2C%20and%20its%20exhaust%20temperature%20rose%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20bring%20the%20part%20of%20the%20plane%20to%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Currie%2C%20the%20only%20other%20surviving%20member%20of%20Mr%20Olver's%20crew%20present%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20discovery%2C%20said%20they%20experienced%20great%20discovery%20in%20pull%20out%20the%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20incredibly%20heavy%20and%20awkward.%20It%20stretched%20out%20the%20net%20and%20ripped%20it.%20It%20was%20too%20big%20to%20get%20up%20on%20the%20deck%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Currie%2C%20now%2069%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fnational%2Fa-trawler-skipper-s-memory-from-the-deep-dredges-up-intriguing-questions-20231214-p5erln.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESydney%20Morning%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20I%20saw%20it%20I%20knew%20what%20it%20was.%20It%20was%20obviously%20a%20wing%2C%20or%20a%20big%20part%20of%20it%2C%20from%20a%20commercial%20plane.%20It%20was%20white%2C%20and%20obviously%20not%20from%20a%20military%20jet%20or%20a%20little%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20members%20on%20the%20trawler%20were%20forced%20to%20cut%20the%20%2420%2C000%20net%20after%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20plane%20piece%20onto%20their%20vessel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Over%20said%20he%20can%20still%20give%20authorities%20the%20coordinates%20of%20where%20he%20discovered%20the%20wing.%20He%20said%20the%20plane's%20part%20came%20to%20rest%20at%20a%20relatively%20shallow%20depth%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20a%20sea%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20area%20is%20about%2055%20kilometres%20west%20of%20the%20South%20Australian%20town%20of%20Robe%2C%20describing%20the%20area%20as%20his%20secret%20trawling%20area%20for%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703066760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fhqeq9us4_mh370-malaysian-airlines_625x300_30_July_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-fisherman-claims-he-found-part-of-mh370-i-wish-id-never-seen-the-thing-4709281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kit%20Olver%20hasn't%20spoken%20about%20it%20for%20years.%20But%20now%2C%20the%2077-year-old%20wants%20the%20world%20to%20hear%20his%20story.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-fisherman-claims-he-found-part-of-mh370-i-wish-id-never-seen-the-thing-4709281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-fisherman-claims-he-found-part-of-mh370-i-wish-id-never-seen-the-thing-4709281%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-fisherman-claims-he-found-part-of-mh370-i-wish-id-never-seen-the-thing-4709281%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boy%20who%20planned%20synagogue%20attack%20in%20US%20ordered%20to%20write%20book%20report%22%2