Wellingborough%2C%20it%20will%20increase%20pressure%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak.%20Sunak%2C%20who%20became%20UK%20leader%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20revive%20the%20party's%20fortunes%20and%20has%20consistently%20trailed%20the%20Labour%20opposition%20in%20polls.%20The%20by-election%2C%20which%20could%20take%20place%20in%20February%2C%20was%20triggered%20after%2010%25%20of%20voters%20signed%20a%20petition%20to%20recall%20Bone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fhttps%2Fexample-com%2Fuk-tories-face-another-by-election-after-mp-ousted-london%2Farticleshow%2F106152055.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fhttps%2Fexample-com%2Fuk-tories-face-another-by-election-after-mp-ousted-london%2Famp_articleshow%2F106152055.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fhttps%2Fexample-com%2Fuk-tories-face-another-by-election-after-mp-ousted-london%2Famp_articleshow%2F106152055.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Agnipath%20Scheme%20Was%20%E2%80%98Bolt%20Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%20for%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%3A%20Former%20Army%20Chief%20Naravane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20141044%2Fnaravane.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Army%20chief%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Agnipath%20tour%20of%20duty%20scheme%20was%20announced%2C%20it%20caught%20the%20Army%20by%20surprise%20and%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbolt%20out%20of%20the%20blue%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20the%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Naravane%20discussed%20the%20contentious%20scheme%20in%20his%20soon-to-be%20memoirs%2C%20titled%20%3Cem%3EFour%20Stars%20of%20Destiny%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fin-his-memoir-gen-naravane-sheds-light-on-how-agnipath-scheme-evolved%2F1890826%2F%5C%22%3Ereviewed%20by%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20General%20Naravane%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Army%20chief%20from%20December%2031%2C%202019%20to%20April%2030%2C%202022%2C%20said%20he%20%E2%80%9Csounded%20out%E2%80%9D%20a%20%E2%80%98Tour%20of%20Duty%E2%80%99%20scheme%20in%20early%202020%20to%20induct%20soldiers%20for%20short-term%20tenure.%20But%20months%20later%2C%20the%20PMO%E2%80%99s%20formulation%20had%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20included%20all%20three%20services%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20in%20the%20army%20were%20taken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20navy%20and%20air%20force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue%2C%E2%80%9D%20General%20Naravane%20wrote.%20He%20had%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%20chiefs%20that%20his%20initial%20proposal%20was%20only%20regarding%20the%20Army%20and%20he%20was%20of%20the%20view%20that%C2%A075%25%20of%20the%20personnel%20recruited%20would%20be%20retained%2C%20while%2025%25%20should%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fdefence-ministry-announces-agnipath-scheme-for-soldier-recruitment%5C%22%3Eannounced%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2014%2C%202022%2C%20it%20said%20only%2025%25%20of%20recruits%20would%20be%20retained%20while%20the%20rest%20would%20be%20released%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20their%20four-year%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20writes%20in%20the%20book%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20had%20first%20sounded%20out%20the%20PM%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20more%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20short-service%20option%20at%20the%20soldier%20level%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20scheme%20for%20officers%20that%20was%20already%20in%20vogue%E2%80%A6.%20Just%20as%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20SSC%20officers%20are%20taken%20each%20year%2C%20likewise%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20jawans%20would%20be%20similarly%20enrolled%20and%20released%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98tour%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20option%20of%20re-enlisting%20for%20another%20tour%2C%20if%20found%20to%20be%20fit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20did%20not%20make%20much%20headway%20initially%20because%20of%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20and%20the%20clashes%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20armies%20in%20Galwan%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20in%20mid-2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20was%20considering%20this%20proposal%20but%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20applicability.%20In%20the%20PMO%20formulation%2C%20not%20only%20should%20the%20complete%20intake%20of%20the%20year%20be%20short-service%20based%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20book%2C%20published%20by%20Penguin%20Random%20House%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20become%20a%20tri-service%20matter%2C%20it%20now%20fell%20on%20Chief%20of%20Defence%20Staff%20Gen%20Bipin%20Rawat%20to%20take%20the%20proposal%20forward%2C%20albeit%20with%20the%20Army%20remaining%20the%20lead%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20book%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20PTI%2C%20General%20Naravane%20wrote%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20for%20a%20first-year%20Agniveer%20was%20initially%20an%20all-inclusive%20Rs%2020%2C000%20per%20month.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20just%20not%20acceptable.%20Here%2C%20we%20were%20talking%20about%20a%20trained%20soldier%20who%20was%20expected%20to%20lay%20down%20his%20life%20for%20the%20country.%20Surely%20a%20soldier%20could%20not%20be%20compared%20with%20a%20daily%20wage%20labourer%3F%20Based%20on%20our%20very%20strong%20recommendations%2C%20this%20was%20later%20raised%20to%20Rs%2030%2C000%20per%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20clashes%20with%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fagnipath-scheme-surprised-army-it-was-a-bolt-out-of-the-blue-for-navy-and-air-force-former-army-chief-writes-in-forthcoming-memoir%2Farticle67655104.ece%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20book%20also%20details%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbehind-the-scenes%20events%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20stand-off%20with%20China%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20in%20mid-2020%2C%20when%20clashes%20between%20the%20two%20armies%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%2021%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20four%20Chinese%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Naravane%20writes%20that%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20told%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20appropriate)%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2031%2C%20terming%20the%20situation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnearing%20breaking%20point%E2%80%9D.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20both%20sides%20had%20moved%20tanks%20near%20Rechin%20La%20on%20the%20south%20bank%20of%20Pangong%20Tso%2C%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20my%20den%20at%20Army%20House%2C%20with%20the%20map%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh%20on%20one%20wall%2C%20Eastern%20Command%20on%20another.%20They%20were%20unmarked%20maps%2C%20but%20as%20I%20looked%20at%20them%2C%20I%20could%20visualise%20the%20location%20of%20each%20and%20every%20unit%20and%20formation.%20We%20were%20ready%20in%20all%20respects%2C%20but%20did%20I%20really%20want%20to%20start%20a%20war%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20country%20was%20in%20bad%20shape%2C%20reeling%20under%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%20The%20economy%20was%20faltering%2C%20global%20supply%20chains%20had%20broken%20down.%20Would%20we%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20a%20steady%20supply%20of%20spares%2C%20etc.%2C%20under%20these%20conditions%2C%20in%20case%20of%20a%20long-drawn-out%20action%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20Who%20were%20our%20supporters%20in%20the%20global%20arena%2C%20and%20what%20about%20the%20collusive%20threat%20from%20China%20and%20Pakistan%3F%20A%20hundred%20different%20thoughts%20flashed%20through%20my%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20moments%20of%20reflection%2C%20he%20called%20up%20the%20then%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20Lt%20General%20Y.K.%20Joshi%20and%20told%20him%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20cannot%20be%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20fire%E2%80%9D%20because%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20provide%20the%20Chinese%20with%20an%20excuse%2C%20a%20casus%20belli%2C%20to%20escalate%20and%20paint%20us%20as%20the%20aggressors%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20I%20told%20him%20to%20move%20a%20troop%20of%20our%20tanks%20right%20to%20the%20forward%20slopes%20of%20the%20Pass%20and%20depress%20their%20guns%20so%20that%20the%20PLA%20would%20be%20staring%20down%20the%20barrels%20of%20our%20guns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20done%20forthwith%20and%20the%20PLA%20tanks%2C%20which%20had%20by%20then%20reached%20within%20a%20few%20hundred%20metres%20of%20the%20top%2C%20stopped%20in%20their%20tracks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20light%20tanks%20would%20have%20been%20no%20match%20for%20our%20medium%20tanks.%20It%20was%20a%20game%20of%20bluff%20and%20the%20PLA%20blinked%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20PLA%20moved%20troops%20from%20Moldo%20to%20the%20area%20of%20Chuti%20Changla%20towards%20the%20south%20bank%20of%20Pangong%20Tso%20on%20the%20intervening%20night%20of%20August%2029-30.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20PLA%20reaction%20was%20not%20long%20in%20coming.%20On%20the%2030th%20evening%20itself%2C%20they%20moved%20forward%20some%20troops%20in%20the%20area%20of%20the%20Kailash%20Range%2C%20stopping%20about%20500%20metres%20short%20of%20our%20locations%20and%20started%20digging%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20PLA%20locations%20were%20at%20lower%20heights%20and%20directly%20under%20Indian%20observation.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20such%2C%20they%20were%20of%20no%20threat%20to%20us%2C%20but%20if%20they%20were%20to%20come%20up%20in%20strength%20and%20try%20to%20outflank%20or%20surround%20our%20localities%2C%20then%20we%20would%20have%20to%20take%20action.%20The%20situation%20was%20tense%20and%20nearing%20breaking%20point.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703064575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20141044%2Fnaravane.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20forthcoming%20memoirs%20titled%20'Four%20Stars%20of%20Destiny'%2C%20General%20Naravane%20says%20that%20he%20had%20initially%20proposed%20a%20four-year%20tour%20of%20duty%20scheme%20only%20for%20the%20Army.%20The%20PMO's%20formulation%20expanded%20it%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Abhishek%20shares%20unseen%20pics%20from%20'Dhoom%203'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703064560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106152020%2Cimgsize-59948.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhishek-bachchan-shares-unseen-pics-from-dhoom-3-as-the-film-completes-10-years%2Farticleshow%2F106152020.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20a