3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106149904.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga's%20'Animal'%20has%20been%20making%20headlines%20ever%20since%20its%20release%20on%20December%201.%20The%20intimate%20scene%20between%20Ranvijay%20(played%20by%20Ranbir%20Kapoor)%20and%20Zoya%20(played%20by%20Triptii)%2C%20has%20become%20a%20talking%20point.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanimal-sandeep-reddy-vanga-reacts-on-ranbir-kapoor-triptii-dimris-intimate-scene%2Farticleshow%2F106149904.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Experts%20Suggest%20Masking%20Up%20in%20Public%20Places%20As%20COVID-19%20Cases%20Rise%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20132717%2FEffect-36.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAmid%20the%20uptick%20in%20COVID-19%20cases%20once%20again%2C%20health%20experts%20suggest%20that%20people%20should%20consider%20wearing%20masks%2C%20especially%20in%20public%20places%2C%20to%20contain%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Tuesday%2C%20December%2019%2C%20the%20number%20of%20active%20cases%20in%20the%20country%20stood%20at%201%2C970%20cases%2C%20with%20Kerala%20accounting%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20infections%20(89%25%20and%201%2C749%20cases).%20Karnataka%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20as%20of%20Wednesday%2C%20December%2020%20morning%2C%20reported%2079%20cases%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2044%20cases%20that%20had%20come%20to%20light%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20health%20minister%2C%20Veena%20George%2C%20on%20Tuesday%20held%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20with%20experts%20and%20government%20officials%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20situation.%20Following%20the%20meeting%2C%20an%20advisory%20was%20issued%20calling%20on%20the%20people%20to%20mask%20up%20in%20public%20places%20whilst%20making%20it%20mandatory%20at%20hospitals%20and%20among%20high-risk%20groups%20and%20public%20health%20experts%2C%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20government%20has%20also%20confirmed%20the%20detection%20of%20the%20new%20COVID%20variant%2C%20JN.1%2C%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20noting%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20panic%2C%20George%20told%20the%20media%20that%20hospital%20staff%2C%20those%20visiting%20hospitals%2C%20those%20with%20serious%20ailments%2C%20and%20pregnant%20women%20should%20wear%20masks.%20It%20was%20also%20resolved%20in%20the%20meeting%20to%20conduct%20Covid-19%20tests%20only%20on%20symptomatic%20patients%2C%20George%20added.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20restriction%20on%20tests%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20attempt%20to%20keep%20the%20number%20of%20positive%20cases%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Kerala%20health%20ministry%2C%201%2C957%20oxygen%20beds%2C%202%2C454%20ICU%20beds%2C%20and%20937%20ICU%20ventilators%20have%20been%20kept%20ready.%20An%20online%20mock%20drill%20involving%201%2C192%20government%20and%20private%20hospitals%20was%20also%20done%20between%20December%2013%20and%2016%2C%20George%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20identified%20upcoming%20Christmas%20and%20New%20Year%20holidays%2C%20the%20Sabarimala%20pilgrimage%2C%20and%20some%20scheduled%20political%20gatherings%20in%20the%20state%20as%20high-risk%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPublic%20health%20experts%20seconded%20the%20caution%20sounded%20by%20the%20minister.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20the%20virulence%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20may%20be%20comparatively%20low%2C%20around%2020%25%20of%20persons%20may%20develop%20post%20Covid-19%20symptoms.%20Hence%2C%20everyone%20must%20wear%20masks%2C%20especially%20in%20closed%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EDH%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20B.%20Ekbal%2C%20a%20public%20health%20expert%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Covid%20Expert%20Committee%20of%20the%20Kerala%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20developing%20situation%2C%20Union%20health%20minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20on%20Wednesday%20also%20held%20a%20review%20meeting%20virtually%20with%20health%20ministers%20and%20additional%20chief%20principal%20secretaries%20(Health)%20of%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20be%20on%20the%20alert%20but%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20panic.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20laxity%20in%20our%20preparedness.%20Health%20is%20not%20an%20area%20for%20any%20politics.%20The%20Union%20Health%20Ministry%20is%20available%20for%20every%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fbe-alert-but-don-t-panic-mandaviya-after-reviewing-covid-19-situation-123122000325_1.html%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Mandaviya%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20suggested%20authorities%20concerned%20carry%20out%20mock%20drills%20at%20hospitals%2C%20increase%20surveillance%2C%20and%20carry%20out%20effective%20communication%20with%20people.%20The%20minister%20said%20preventive%20measures%20should%20be%20in%20place%20to%20arrest%20the%20spread%20of%20infections%20in%20the%20upcoming%20festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20assessment%20issued%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20for%20the%20new%20subvariant%2C%20the%20overall%20risk%20assessment%20remains%20low.%20There%20is%20no%20change%20in%20the%20disease%20pattern.%20It%20has%20said%20considering%20that%20a%20number%20of%20countries%20would%20be%20entering%20winter%20season%2C%20so%20respiratory%20infections%2C%20including%20Covid-19%2C%20may%20see%20a%20rise.%20India%20last%20year%20too%20witnessed%20a%20small%20surge%2