0irritant%20for%20those%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Fagri-business%2Finspector-raj-re-emerges-as-centres-wheat-stockholding-limit-order-turns-ammunition-against-processors%2Farticle67655086.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20BusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20December%208%20tightened%20the%20stocking%20norms%20for%20retailers%2C%20wholesalers%2C%20and%20processors.%20According%20to%20these%20norms%2C%20any%20retail%20outlet%2C%20including%20big%20chains%20at%20the%20retail%20outlet%20level%2C%20can%20stock%20up%20to%20five%20tonnes%20of%20wheat%20limit%2C%20as%20against%20the%20earlier%2010-tonne%20ceiling.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20traders%20and%20wholesalers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20big%20chain%20retailers%20at%20depot%20level%2C%20the%20limit%20has%20been%20cut%20from%202%2C000%20tonnes%20to%201%2C000%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20in%20the%20case%20of%20processors%20of%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eatta%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%20other%20flour%20products%20like%3Ci%3E%C2%A0sooji%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Eand%C2%A0%3Ci%3Emaida%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20the%20maximum%20capacity%20will%20be%2070%25%20of%20the%20monthly%20installed%20capacity%20of%20the%20mills%20multiplied%20by%20four%2C%20which%20is%20the%20remaining%20months%20of%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20food%20ministry%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20all%20stakeholders%20involved%20to%20adhere%20to%20their%20respective%20stocking%20limits%20by%20January%206%2C%202024%2C%20in%20case%20the%20stocks%20held%20by%20them%20are%20higher%20than%20the%20restricted%20limits.%20Additionally%2C%20wheat%20stocking%20entities%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20register%20themselves%20on%20the%20wheat%20stock%20limit%20portal%20and%20update%20the%20stock%20position%20every%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20speculation%20that%20the%20government%20may%20ease%20existing%20norms%20depending%20on%20the%20reduction%20in%20supplies%20available%20in%20the%20market%20eventually%20with%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20season%20in%20April.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20easing%20of%20norms%20may%20first%20benefit%20processors%20from%20February%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20stock%20more%20as%20produce%20from%20the%20new%20crop%20starts%20arriving%20in%20the%20market%20from%20mid-February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20relaxation%20in%20norms%20may%20come%20later%2C%20those%20affected%20by%20inspections%20suggest%20authorities%20concerned%20first%20gather%20inputs%20and%20then%20send%20officials%20for%20inspection.%20Some%20of%20the%20mill%20owners%20and%20traders%20are%20said%20to%20have%20conveyed%20the%20same%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703054126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19161235%2F31764443254_73b92a3ef0_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwheat-traders-processors-upset-over-frequent-inspections-for-enforcing-stocking-norms-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20on%20December%208%20tightened%20the%20stocking%20norms%20for%20wheat%20retailers%2C%20wholesalers%2C%20and%20processors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fwheat-traders-processors-upset-over-frequent-inspections-for-enforcing-stocking-norms-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20borrows%20%24120%20million%20from%20Japan's%20SMBC%20to%20buy%20Airbus%20plane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703053229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fassets%2Fweb-assets%2Fimages%2FBusiness_Standard_685x385.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-india-borrows-120-million-from-japan-s-smbc-to-buy-airbus-plane-12312200027