vernment%2F141-here-are-all-the-mps-suspended-from-parliament-this-winter-session%5C%22%3E143%20MPs%20have%20been%20suspended%20over%20the%20past%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20demanding%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20breach%20of%20security%20at%20parliament%20on%20December%2013.%20The%20unprecedented%20numbers%20have%20left%20lakhs%20of%20electors%20across%20the%20country%20without%20a%20voice%2C%20while%20some%20parties%20have%20been%20shorn%20of%20their%20presence%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20MPs%20are%20suspended%20for%20demanding%20accountability%2C%20a%20little%20more%20of%20democracy%20is%20sucked%20out%20from%20an%20%E2%80%98electoral%20autocracy%E2%80%99%20that%20is%20increasingly%20paying%20attention%20to%20throttling%20independent%20institutions%2C%20whose%20health%20is%20what%20democracies%20rest%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Wire%20calculates%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20suspensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectors%20denied%20their%20voice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20India%20does%20not%20have%20a%20system%20of%20proportional%20representation%2C%20the%20MPs%20reflect%20the%20voices%20and%20concerns%20of%20their%20electors.%20After%20the%20suspensions%2C%2014%2C76%2C98%2C507%20electors%20from%2094%20constituencies%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F5WLys%2F2%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Electors%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20representative%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22995%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20was%20dire%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20to%20estimate%20the%20number%20of%20electors%20muted%20via%20these%20suspensions%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20divided%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electors%20in%20a%20state%20by%20the%20number%20of%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20that%20state%20has%2C%20as%20a%20broad%20average%20of%20electors%20each%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20represents.%20By%20adding%20these%20numbers%2C%20depending%20upon%20the%20number%20of%20suspensions%20from%20the%20state%2C%20we%20again%20can%20get%20an%20approximation%20of%20the%20number%20of%20voices%20put%20away%20by%20suspending%20their%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20that%20we%20arrive%20at%20through%20this%20calculation%20is%2018%2C43%2C83%2C909%20(18.43%20crore)%20electors%20who%20have%20been%20denied%20a%20voice%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20through%20the%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fjk2Hv%2F1%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Suspended%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20and%20their%20electors%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221246%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParties%20severely%20depleted%2C%20some%20go%20missing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20the%20MPs%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20session%20has%20severely%20affected%20the%20presence%20of%20major%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20two%20houses%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20strength%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20quarter.%20Other%20parties%20like%20the%20DMK%2C%20TMC%20and%20JDU%20have%20seen%20their%20strength%20deplete%20by%20over%2060%25.%20The%20AAP%20has%20no%20representative%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20anymore%2C%20while%20some%20smaller%20parties%20have%20also%20lost%20their%20representatives%20completely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F61rbE%2F3%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Remaining%20strength%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20too%2C%20the%20strength%20of%20major%20opposition%20parties%20was%20greatly%20depleted.%20The%20Congress%20was%20down%20to%20a%20fourth%20of%20its%20strength%20as%20was%20the%20TMC%2C%20while%20the%20DMK%20was%20cut%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FILHF0%2F2%2F%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Remaining%20strength%20of%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIssues%20raised%20by%20MPs%20were%20scotched%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2071%20Questions%20asked%20by%20them%20are%20deleted%20or%20cancelled%2C%20noted%20Maadhyam%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20watchdog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20total%20of%2027%20Questions%20are%20deleted%2C%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%2044%20Questions%20are%20cancelled.%20Govt%20manages%20to%20escape%20answering%20these%20Qs.%20It%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20MPs%20submitted%20notices%20of%20these%20Qs%20much%20before%20their%20suspension%20(notice%20period%20for%20a%20Q%20is%2015%20days).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20government%20time%20is%20%E2%80%93%20and%20rightly%20so%20%E2%80%93%20spent%20on%20answering%20questions%20raised%20by%20MPs.%20With%20a%20data-deficient%20regime%20in%20place%2C%20where%20there%20is%20also%20a%20good%20deal%20of%20data%20evasion%20and%20manipulation%2C%20parliamentary%20questions%20and%20answers%20are%20often%20a%20key%20data%20resource%20and%20enable%20the%20principle%20of%20accountability%20to%20seep%20into%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaadhyam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20were%20listed%20for%20answering%20today%2C%20it%20means%20that%20these%20Qs%20successfully%20made%20it%20through%20a%20ballot%20and%20were%20admitted%20for%20answering.%20The%20Ministry%20would%20have%20also%20prepared%20the%20responses%20by%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20it%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMPs%20don%E2%80%99t%20ask%20these%20Qs%20for%20themselves%2C%20they%20ask%20these%20Qs%20for%20us%2C%20on%20our%20behalf.%20The%20information%20given%20in%20response%20to%20these%20Qs%2C%20is%20public%20information%20and%20not%20meant%20for%20private%20consumption%20of%20the%20MP.%20Deleting%20or%20cancelling%20of%20Qs%20also%20deprive%20people%20of%20getting%20this%20information.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%20and%20Amrit%20B.L.S.%20Visualisation%20by%20Amrit%20B.L.S.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20updated%20after%20Thomas%20Chazhikadan%20and%20A.M.%20Ariff%20were%20suspended%20on%20December%2020.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703051182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20111531%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20some%20parties%20have%20been%20robbed%20of%20a%20presence%20in%20parliament%2C%20it%20is%20the%20people%20who%20suffer.%20The%20Wire%20measures%20just%20how%20much.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcost-of-suspending-members-of-parliament%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Panders%20to%20Rightwing'%3A%20France%20Passes%20New%2C%20'Strict'%20Immigration%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20110131%2FGA0_RMiWIAA5UR0.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20in%20the%20French%20parliament%20passed%20legislation%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20will%20bring%20in%20stricter%20controls%20on%20migration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20had%20been%20facing%20a%20rebellion%20from%20within%20his%20party%20after%20the%20bill%20won%20support%20from%20the%20far-right%20National%20Rally%20(RN)%2C%20led%20by%20Marine%20Le%20Pen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20passed%20through%20the%20lower%20house%20with%20votes%20from%20Macron%E2%80%99s%20centrist%20coalition%20and%20conservative%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterior%20Minister%20Gerald%20Darmanin%20%E2%80%94%20who%20had%20spearheaded%20the%20bill%20%E2%80%94%20expressed%20relief%20after%20a%20large%20majority%20voted%20in%20favour%2C%20meaning%20it%20no%20longer%20depended%20on%20the%20support%20from%20those%20far-right%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20subject%20of%20immigration%20is%20a%20major%20political%20plank%20for%20the%20upcoming%20parliamentary%20elections.%20While%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20bill%20would%20have%20favoured%20Macron%2C%20the%20support%20shown%20by%20Le%20Pen%20%E2%80%94%20who%20called%20the%20stricter%20bill%20%E2%80%9Ca%20great%20ideological%20victory%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20far-right%20%E2%80%94%20can%20also%20improve%20her%20chances%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20new%20immigration%20law%20entail%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20bill%20was%20first%20submitted%2C%20it%20has%20seen%20various%20amendments%20toughening%20the%20immigration%20rules%2C%20with%20the%20left%20accusing%20the%20government%20of%20giving%20in%20to%20the%20pressure%20from%20the%20far-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20legislation%20more%20agreeable%20for%20the%20right%2C%20the%20government%20decided%20to%20weaken%20measures%20that%20would%20have%20allowed%20some%20immigrants%20residency%20permits.%20The%20government%20also%20agreed%20to%20extend%20the%20duration%20of%20stay%20in%20France%20for%20migrants%20to%20be%20eligible%20to%20access%20welfare%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20new%20legislation%2C%20access%20to%20housing%20benefits%20will%20be%20also%20be%20delayed%20for%20unemployed%20non-EU%20migrants%20by%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20gain%20the%20support%20of%20the%20right%2C%20the%20government%20has%20also%20introduced%20migration%20quotas%20which%20will%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20immigrants%E2%80%99%20children%20to%20become%20French.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20now%20it%20will%20be%20easier%20for%20migrants%20working%20in%20sectors%20that%20lack%20labour%20to%20get%20a%20residency%20permit%2C%20it%20will%20also%20be%20easier%20to%20expel%20illegal%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrance-passes-controversial-immigration-bill%2Fa-67772998%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703050809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F20110131%2FGA0_RMiWIAA5UR0.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpanders-to-rightwing-france-passes-new-strict-immigration-bill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20aimed%20at%20tightening%20immigration%20rules%20was%20passed%20without%20the%20need%20for%20far-right%20votes%2C%20despite%20major%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpanders-to-rightwing-france-passes-new-strict-immigration-bill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Descendants%20fight%20to%20maintain%20historic%20Black%20communities.%20Keeping%20their%20legacy%20alive%20is%20complicated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703050718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106145044%2Cimgsize-1184234.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdescendants-fight-to-maintain-historic-black-communities-keeping-their-legacy-alive-is-complicated%2Farticleshow%2F106143950.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%2