%20of%20domesticated%20animals.%20Milk%20would%20often%20be%20in%20excess.%20The%20farmer%20decided%20to%20put%20this%20to%20use%20and%20began%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252594%2Fchitale-bandhu-mithai-bakarwadi-babasaheb-bhaskar-ganesh-chitale-shrikhand-mango-burfi-peda-indian-icons-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20cottage%20cheese%2C%20shrikhand%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20over%2040%2C000%20farmers%20work%20with%20the%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bakarwadi%20sold%20by%20the%20brand%20is%20so%20famous%20that%20over%201%2C000%20kgs%20are%20made%20in%20an%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Vadilal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20all%20enjoyed%20the%20popsicles%20on%20a%20sunny%20afternoon%20after%20the%20end-of-year%20exams.%20The%20name%20%E2%80%98Vadilal%E2%80%99%20evokes%20nostalgia.%20The%20brand%20had%20humble%20beginnings%20in%20Gujarat%20in%201907.%20At%20the%20time%20their%20ice%20creams%20were%20made%20using%20the%20traditional%20and%20popular%20Kothi%20method%20in%20which%20a%20hand-operated%20machine%20was%20used%20to%20churn%20milk%2C%20ice%20and%20salt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVadilal%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271527%2Fcentury-old-vadilal-ice-cream-brand-first-to-launch-dollies-cones%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20the%20brand%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sodas%20but%20it%20was%20his%20son%20Ranchod%20Lal%20Gandhi%20who%20introduced%20ice%20creams%20to%20the%20brand.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%2C%20the%20company%20had%20opened%20four%20outlets%20across%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20company%20clocked%20a%20turnover%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C%20071%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E