0river-like%20environment%20to%20thrive.%20To%20ensure%20this%2C%20you%20must%20introduce%20algae%20inside%20the%20pond.%20Algae%20is%20the%20major%20food%20source%20of%20an%20oyster%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20pH%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESanjay%20points%20out%20that%20farmers%20should%20ensure%20a%20pH%20of%20eight%20inside%20the%20water%20tank.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20pH%20is%20more%20than%20eight%20(alkaline)%2C%20oysters%20will%20not%20survive.%20You%20should%20also%20check%20pH%20levels%20weekly.%20If%20the%20pH%20is%20higher%2C%20keep%20changing%20the%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20have%20a%2020%C3%9720%20square%20feet%20pond%20with%2010%20feet%20depth%2C%20it%20would%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20store%20one%20lakh%20litre%20water.%20So%2C%20you%20should%20replace%20at%20least%2010%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20every%20batch%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaintain%20the%20temperature%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiven%20its%20geography%2C%20Sanjay%20says%20that%20Osmanabad%20has%20a%20fluctuating%20temperature%20between%2020%20and%2040%20degrees%20throughout%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20oyster%20pearl%20farming%2C%20we%20must%20ensure%20a%20temperature%20of%2032%20degrees%20Celsius.%20It%20should%20not%20exceed%2035%20degrees.%20We%20have%20externally%20used%20aerators%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20inside%20the%20water%20bank.%20It%20also%20boosts%20fresh%20algae%20growth%20and%20provides%20new%20micronutrients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Sanjay%20Pawar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700662267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Foyster-5-1700660441.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D334671%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20incurred%20huge%20losses%20because%20of%20recurring%