E2%80%99d%20only%20managed%20to%20attempt%2030.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20%E2%80%94%20famous%20for%20scoring%20a%20perfect%20360%2F360%20in%20the%20JEE%20Mains%202017%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20recalls%20that%20moment%20in%20time%2C%20he%20terms%20it%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elife-changing%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Although%20flustered%2C%20he%20felt%20he%20knew%20his%20attitude%20determined%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20set%20my%20pen%20down%20and%20closed%20my%20eyes.%20I%20recalled%20all%20the%20exams%20I%20had%20ever%20attempted.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20how%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20I%E2%80%99d%20risen%20from%20a%20nobody%20to%20a%20ranker.%20Then%2C%20I%20picked%20my%20pen%20up%20and%20started%20solving%20again.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20next%20one%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20went%20by%20is%20a%20blur%20in%20Kalpit%E2%80%99s%20memory.%20But%20when%20the%20bell%20went%20off%2C%20he%20was%20done%20with%20every%20question.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20day%20to%20the%20present%2C%20the%2024-year-old%20Udaipur%20native%E2%80%99s%20journey%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20unconventional.%20Ask%20him%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332971%2Fbrillio-national-stem-learning-challenge-government-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosely-guarded%20secret%20to%20success%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20he%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20isn%E2%80%99t%20one.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20of%20relentless%20hard%20work%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20middle-class%20home%2